nt%E2%80%99s%20Failures%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08133122%2FModi-Kharge.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Congress%20on%20Thursday%20(February%208)%20released%20a%20black%20paper%20on%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20failures%2C%20highlighting%20economic%2C%20social%20and%20political%20injustices%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2054-page%20document%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3E10%20Saal%20Anyay%20Kal%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20released%20by%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20claims%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20its%20ten%20years%20in%20power%20has%20%E2%80%9Cdevastated%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economy%2C%20aggravated%20unemployment%2C%20destroyed%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20agricultural%20sector%2C%20abetted%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20committed%20grave%20injustices%20against%20minorities%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20we%20are%20bringing%20out%20a%20%E2%80%98Black%20Paper%E2%80%99%20against%20the%20government.%20Whenever%20PM%20Modi%20presents%20his%20views%20in%20Parliament%2C%20he%20hides%20his%20failures.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20when%20we%20speak%20about%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20government%2C%20it%20is%20not%20given%20importance.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20want%20to%20bring%20out%20a%20Black%20Paper%20and%20tell%20the%20public%20about%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20to%20release%20the%20%E2%80%9Cblack%20paper%E2%80%9D%20comes%20amid%20speculation%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20will%20bring%20a%20white%20paper%20in%20parliament%20to%20highlight%20the%20economic%20failures%20of%20the%20UPA%20between%202004%20and%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Jayant%20Sinha%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20member%20of%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Finance%2C%20said%20that%20a%20white%20paper%20will%20be%20brought%20to%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20GDP%20growth%20had%20slowed%20down%20to%205%25%2C%20inflation%20had%20risen%20to%2010%25%2C%20The%20country%20was%20facing%20a%20balance%20of%20payment%20crisis.%20The%20baking%20system%20was%20in%20a%20crisis.%20Everyone%20was%20leaving%20the%20country%20and%20we%20were%20in%20the%20fragile%20economies%20in%20the%20world.%20This%20is%20the%20condition%20in%20which%20the%20UPA%20had%20left%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20his%20remarks%20on%20the%20interim%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20white%20paper%2C%20we%20will%20clarify%20what%20was%20the%20position%20of%20the%20economy%20(before%202014)%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20how%20we%20have%20tackled%20the%20economic%20problems.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20interim%20budget%20session%20of%20parliament%20which%20was%20slated%20to%20end%20on%20Friday%20has%20also%20been%20extended%20by%20a%20day%20to%20Saturday%2C%20when%20the%20white%20paper%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20presented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Black%20Paper%20claims%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20%E2%80%9Cblack%20paper%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20years%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cmarked%20by%20high%20rates%20of%20unemployment%2C%20economic%20catastrophes%20such%20as%20demonetisation%20and%20flawed%20GST%2C%20which%20have%20only%20increased%20the%20divide%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20poor%20and%20devastated%20the%20future%20of%20millions%20of%20farmers%20and%20daily%20wage%20workers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20highlighted%20the%20highest%20unemployment%20rate%20in%2045%20years%2C%20prices%20of%20essential%20commodities%20being%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%2C%20and%20failure%20to%20increase%20MSP%20for%20farmers%20despite%20a%20promise%20to%20double%20their%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerming%20it%20%E2%80%9CModani%20Raj%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20party%20has%20also%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9Cneutering%E2%80%9D%20investigative%20agencies%20despite%20a%20promise%20to%20eliminate%20safe%20havens%C2%A0%20for%20economic%20offenders%20and%20facilitating%20crony%20capitalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20%3Cem%3Esamajik%20anyay%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20social%20injustice%2C%20the%20party%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20last%20decade%20has%20seen%20%E2%80%9Cblatant%20discrimination%20and%20severe%20oppression%20against%20women%2C%20SC%2CSTs%2COBCs%20and%20minorities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIts%20politics%20of%20hatred%2C%20polarisation%20and%20divide%20has%20destroyed%20the%20social%20fabric%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20document%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20%3Cem%3Erajneetik%20anyay%3C%2Fem%3E%20(political%20injustice)%20the%20Congress%20has%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20remaining%20silent%20on%20China%E2%80%99s%20encroachments%20on%20Indian%20territory%2C%20%E2%80%9Cundermining%20the%20Army%20with%20the%20Agneepath%20scheme%E2%80%9D%20and%20targeting%20opposition%20with%20its%20investigative%20agencies%20and%20%E2%80%9Cending%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20media%E2%80%9D%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20ED%20and%20RBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CModi%20government%20talks%20about%20Nehru%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20never%20talks%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbiggest%20issue%20in%20the%20country%20which%20is%20unemployment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnarendra-modi-caste-nehru-rajya-sabha%5C%22%3E%20talk%20about%20Nehru%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20talk%20about%20how%20many%20people%20were%20given%20jobs%20through%20public%20sector%20jobs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20ongoing%20protests%20by%20non-BJP%20state%20governments%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20against%20%E2%80%9Ctax%20injustice%E2%80%9D%2C%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20does%20not%20release%20funds%20to%20states%20and%20then%20accuses%20them%20of%20not%20spending%20the%20money%20released%20by%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20jibe%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20he%20had%20given%20rights%20to%20SC%2FST%2FOBCs%2C%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20UPA%20government%20had%20also%20given%20them%20rights%20but%20does%20not%20want%20to%20list%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20are%20emotional%20issues.%20But%20giving%20employment%20is%20important.%20He%20should%20talk%20about%20it.%20You%20can%20talk%20about%20social%20justice%20when%20everyone%20has%20a%20share%20in%20development.%20Why%20are%20we%20insisting%20on%20the%20public%20sector%3F%20When%20PSUs%20are%20formed%2C%20SC-ST%2C%20OBC%20and%20tribals%20get%20employment%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20run%20around%20for%20daily%20wage%20jobs.%20It%20gives%20them%20stability.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20have%20steady%20jobs%20in%20government%20jobs%20and%20the%20public%20sector%20and%20if%20small%20scale%20industries%20have%20to%20be%20established%2C%20they%20should%20be%20hand%20held%20like%20they%20are%20given%20to%20big%20capitalists%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20added%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20ensured%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20and%20in%202024%2C%20it%20will%20take%20the%20country%20out%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cdarkness%20of%20injustice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%20his%20farewell%20speech%20for%20the%20retiring%20members%20of%20the%20House%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20black%20paper%20was%20like%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekaala%20teeka%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20for%20his%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20Khargeji%20has%20come%20I%20have%20to%20fulfill%20my%20dharma%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20child%20gets%20ready%20for%20an%20occasion%20and%20wears%20nice%20clothes%2C%20we%20put%20a%20kaala%20tika%20to%20ward%20off%20evil%20eye.%20Today%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20the%20country%20is%20stepping%20on%20new%20steps%20of%20development.%20That%20is%20why%20I%20thank%20Khargeji%20for%20giving%20this%20kaala%20teeka%20today%20for%20our%20government.%20I%20thought%20people%20will%20come%20in%20black%20clothes%20today%20but%20they%20have%20gone%20up%20to%20a%20black%20paper%20now.%20But%20I%20welcome%20that%20as%20well.%20Because%20whenever%20something%20good%20happens%2C%20kaala%20teeka%20is%20necessary.%20And%20if%20an%20aged%20person%20like%20Khargeji%20does%20it%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20even%20more%20welcome%20for%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707379763000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08133122%2FModi-Kharge.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-releases-black-paper-on-modi-governments-failures%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2054-page%20document%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the%20buzz%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20will%20put%20out%20a%20'White%20Paper'%20making%20comparisons%20with%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20tenure.%20The%20paper%20claims%20that%20ten%20years%20devastated%20the%20country's%20economy%2C%20aggravated%20unemployment%2C%20destroyed%20the%20country's%20agricultural%20sector%2C%20%26quot%3Babetted%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20committed%20grave%20injustices%20against%20minorities%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-releases-black-paper-on-modi-governments-fa