ds%20for%20trying%20to%20keep%20their%20newly%20launched%20cereals%20off%20store%20shelves.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c46b557a3d27148878ea56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESnoop%20Dogg's%20food%20company%20is%20suing%20Walmart%20and%20Post%20Consumer%20Brands%20for%20trying%20to%20keep%20their%20newly%20launched%20cereals%20off%20store%20shelves.%3Cp%3ERodin%20Eckenroth%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Jakub%20Porzycki%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESnoop%20Dogg's%20food%20company%20is%20suing%20Walmart%20and%20Post%20Consumer%20Brands%20for%20their%C2%A0%26quot%3Bdiabolical%20actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20rapper%20accused%20the%20two%20companies%20of%20keeping%C2%A0%26quot%3BSnoop%20Cereal%26quot%3B%20off%20Walmart's%20shelves.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lawsuit%20claimed%20that%20the%20cereal%20was%20being%20intentionally%20kept%20in%20Walmart's%20stockrooms.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESnoop%20Dogg%20and%20his%20fellow%20rapper%20Master%20P%20are%20accusing%20Walmart%20and%20Post%20Consumer%20Brands%20of%20colluding%20to%20keep%20their%20newly%20launched%20cereals%20off%20store%20shelves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rappers'%20attorney%20Ben%20Crump%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbencrump.com%2Fpress%2Fattorney-ben-crump-files-lawsuit-against-walmart-and-post-foods-on-behalf-of-snoop-doggs-and-master-ps-company-broadus-foods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20accused%20Walmart%20of%20colluding%20with%20Post%20Consumer%20Brands.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Crump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbencrump.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FComplaint-Accepted-Filing.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiling%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20two%20companies%20intentionally%20kept%20the%20rappers'%20cereal%20in%20Walmart's%20s