0and%20Renewable%20Energy%20to%20facilitate%20visas%20for%20foreign%20experts%20or%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Chinese%20Charge%20D%E2%80%99Affaires%20Ma%20Jia%20has%20said%20that%20the%20growth%20in%20trade%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20to%20US%20%24136.2%20billion%20%E2%80%93%20went%20along%20with%20other%20areas%20of%20%E2%80%9Cimprovement%E2%80%9D%20in%20bilateral%20ties%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2FEconomy%2Findia-china-bilateral-trade-hit-a-new-record-in-2023-envoy%2Farticle67822802.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%25202022%252C%2520bilateral%2520trade%2520had%2Cof%2520Actual%2520Control%2520(LAC).%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20bilateral%20trade%20had%20reached%20a%20record%20high%20of%20%24135.98%20billion%2C%20while%20the%20trade%20deficit%20in%20favour%20of%20China%20had%20crossed%20%24100%20billion%2C%20driven%20by%20a%2021%25%20rise%20in%20imports%20from%20China%20into%20India%2C%20this%20report%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20exports%20to%20China%20also%20increased%20by%206%25%20last%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ma%20added%20at%20the%20new%20year%20event%20she%20spoke%20at%20on%20February%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMa%20highlighted%20the%20%E2%80%9Cimportant%20consensus%E2%80%9D%20reached%20by%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20bilateral%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20tensions%20remain%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20after%20the%202020%20fight%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20and%20as%3Cem%3E%20The%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20notes%2C%C2%A0China%20has%20not%20appointed%20an%20Ambassador%20to%20Delhi%20in%20over%2016%20months%2C%20the%20longest%20such%20period%20thus%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-artid%3D%5C%2267822802%5C%22%20data-title%3D%5C%22India-China%20bilateral%20trade%20hit%20a%20new%20record%20in%202023%3A%20Envoy%5C%22%20data-url%3D%5C%22https%3A