easures%20in%20Eagle%20Pass.%3Cp%3ELokman%20Vural%20Elibol%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20FBI%20accused%20Paul%20Faye%20Sr.%20of%20planning%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20southern%20border.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20his%20son%2C%20Joseph%20Faye%20says%20his%20father%20only%C2%A0%26quot%3Btalks%20a%20big%20game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFaye%20said%20he'd%20warned%20his%20father%20about%20undercover%20agents%2C%20but%20Faye%20Sr.%20didn't%20listen.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20son%20of%20a%20man%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-arrest-militia-sniper-planning-attack-southern-border-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccused%20of%20planning%20a%20violent%20attack%20on%20the%20southern%20border%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20his%20father%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bcompulsive%20liar%26quot%3B%20who%20%26quot%3Btalks%20a%20big%20game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20a%20terrorist%2C%26quot%3B%20Joseph%20Faye%2C%2030%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Ftennessee-sniper-border-arrest-paul-faye-son-rcna137744%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BHe%20talks%20a%20big%20game%2C%20but%20it's%20all%20lies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFaye's%20father%2C%20Paul%20Faye%20Sr.%2C%20was%20charged%20with%20the%20possession%20of%20an%20unregistered%20silencer%20under%20the%20National%20Firearms%20Act%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24409164-paul-faye-sr-criminal-complaint-case-no-24-mj-1036%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriminal%20complaint%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20on%20February%202.%20Faye%20Sr.%20was%20accused%20of%20trying%20to%20sell%20an%20unregistered%20AK-47%20suppressor%20to%20an%20undercover%20FBI%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20criminal%20complaint%2C%20the%20undercover%20FBI%20agent%20befriended%20Faye%20Sr.%20via%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFaye%20subsequently%20told%20three%20undercover%20agents%20at%20a%20meeting%20in%20April%20that%20he%20believed%20the%20federal%20government%20was%20letting%20illegal%20immigrants%20through%20the%20southern%20border%20on%20purpose%2C%20per%20the%20document.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20criminal%20complaint%2C%20Faye%20Sr.%20subsequently%20outlined%20his%20plans%20to%20attack%20the%20southern%20border.%20He%20told%20an%20agent%20that%20he%20planned%20to%20transport%20explosives%20to%20the%20border%20and%20that%20he%20would%20act%20as%20a%20sniper%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20on%20top%20that%20roof%20right%20there%2C%20zeroing%20out%2C%20taking%20out%20anybody%2C%26quot%3B%20Faye%20Sr.%20told%20an%20undercover%20agent%20during%20a%20meeting%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Faye%20Sr.'s%20son%20says%20his%20father%20isn't%20much%20of%20a%20marksman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20went%20hunting%2C%20and%20my%20dad%20had%20to%20shoot%20at%20a%20deer%20standing%20still%20three%20different%20times%20before%20he%20hit%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Joseph%20Faye%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20a%20sniper.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20younger%20Faye%20said%20that%20most%20of%20the%20weapons%20in%20his%20father's%20%26quot%3Bwar%20room%26quot%3B%20belonged%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20criminal%20complaint%2C%20undercover%20agents%20spotted%20numerous%20firearms%2C%20including%20a%20Creedmoor%20rifle%2C%20several%20AR-15%20rifles%2C%20and%20a%20shotgun%20when%20they%20visited%20him%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20deer%20hunter.%20I%20have%20hunting%20rifles.%20The%20only%20gun%20my%20father%20owns%20is%20an%20old%20shotgun%20he%20got%20from%20his%20dad%20before%20he%20died%2C%26quot%3B%20Joseph%20Faye%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20younger%20Faye%20said%20he'd%20long%20suspected%20his%