C%20as%20a%20nod%20to%20lunge%20at%20Imran%20Khan.%20In%20April%202022%2C%20a%20rainbow%20coalition%20called%20the%20Pakistan%20Democratic%20Movement%20(PDM)%2C%20which%20included%20parties%20like%20the%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PMLN)%20and%20Jamiat-e-Ulama-e-Islam%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20(PPP)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fas-imran-loses-trust-vote-shehbaz-sharif-emerges-frontrunner-for-pak-pms-post%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fas-imran-loses-trust-vote-shehbaz-sharif-emerges-frontrunner-for-pak-pms-post%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707374941341000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1P5793HefhdJBqY35T7sCe%5C%22%3Eousted%20Imran%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20his%20Pakistan%20Tehrik-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20party%E2%80%99s%20government%20through%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fimran-khan-pakistan-democracy%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fimran-khan-pakistan-democracy%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707374941341000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1wtykKZAPQyVj1SJ1Apoif%5C%22%3Eno-confidence%20vote%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20National%20Assembly.%20PMLN%E2%80%99s%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20became%20the%20PDM%20government%E2%80%99s%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImran%20Khan%2C%20however%2C%20trained%20his%20guns%20on%20General%20Bajwa%2C%20holding%20him%20responsible%20for%20his%20downfall.%20He%20also%20tried%20unsuccessfully%20to%20forestall%20General%20Asim%20Munir%20%E2%80%93%20whom%20he%20had%20removed%20as%20the%20DG%20ISI%20%E2%80%93becoming%20the%20new%20COAS.%20While%20this%20escalated%20tensions%20between%20Imran%20Khan%20and%20the%20brass%2C%20the%20latter%20remained%20rather%20restrained.%20But%20all%20hell%20broke%20loose%20when%20on%20May%209%2C%202023%2C%20the%20PTI%20leaders%20and%20workers%20rioted%20against%20military%20installations%20after%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20arrest.%20Imran%20Khan%20seemed%20to%20have%20calculated%20that%20with%20pockets%20of%20support%20within%20the%20army%2C%20judiciary%2C%20and%20general%20public%2C%20he%20could%20bring%20down%20the%20army%20chief%20through%20a%20coterie%20of%20generals%20allied%20with%20him%20and%20also%20upstage%20the%20PDM%20government.%20It%20was%20a%20monumental%20miscalculation%20and%20misreading%20of%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20discipline%20and%20unity%20of%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20cracked%20its%20whip%20and%20thousands%20of%20PTI%20cadres%20and%20leaders%20were%20arrested.%20Imran%20Khan%20himself%20was%20rearrested%20and%20has%20remained%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F9%2F27%2Fpakistan-ex-pm-imran-khan-moved-to-another-jail-after-custody-extended%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F9%2F27%2Fpakistan-ex-pm-imran-khan-moved-to-another-jail-after-custody-extended%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707374941341000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3-FLN7SDXZld3JMmyIqjfg%5C%22%3E%C2%A0incarcerated%3C%2Fa%3E%20since.%20Scores%20of%20PTI%20leaders%20were%20forced%20to%20repent%20and%20pledge%20allegiance%20to%20the%20army%20publicly%20and%20quit%20the%20party.%20Independent%20political%20groupings%20and%20even%20a%20new%20party%20were%20carved%20out%20of%20the%20PTI.%20Imran%20Khan%20went%20from%20being%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20darling%20to%20its%20detested%20demon.%20But%20he%20remained%20popular%20with%20his%20cult-like%20followers%2C%20something%20which%20worried%20the%20brass%20deeply.%20The%20PDM%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20dismal%20economic%20performance%2C%20lacklustre%20leadership%20like%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20and%20total%20subservience%20to%20the%20junta%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20exactly%20capture%20the%20public%20imagination.%20The%20generals%20and%20the%20PDM%2C%20which%20vi