0Iger%20announced%20a%20strong%20start%20to%20the%20year%20for%20Disney%2C%20beating%20Wall%20Street's%20expectations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20returning%20CEO%20had%20faced%20challenges%20during%20his%20first%20year%20back%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20laid%20out%20a%20slate%20of%20new%20partnerships%2C%20including%20with%20Epic%20Games%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-stream-disney-plus-bonus-songs-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbob-iger-ceo-disney-return-insiders-anxious-losing-faith-2023-11%3FIR%3DC%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBob%20Iger's%20return%20to%20Disney%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20starting%20to%20look%20a%20little%20more%20like%20a%20victory%20lap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20challenging%20first%20year%20back%20at%20the%20House%20of%20Mouse%2C%20things%20are%20now%20looking%20rosier%2C%20with%20CEO%20Iger%20pairing%20a%20strong%20earnings%20report%20%3Cspan%3Ewith%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ea%20slate%20of%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eannouncements%3Cspan%3E%2C%20including%20partnerships%20with%20Epic%20Games%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20a%20forthcoming%20sports%20streaming%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20robust%20results%20should%20give%20the%20notably%20confident%20Iger%20ammunition%20in%20his%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-ceo-bob-iger-power-move-trian-peltz-proxy-fight-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebattle%20with%20activist%20shareholders%2C%20including%20Nelson%20Peltz%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20have%20criticized%20Disney%20for%20its%20lagging%20stock%20performance%20and%20for%20ex-leader%20Bob%20Chapek's%20short%20and%20rocky%20tenure%20before%20Iger%20returned%20in%20late%202022.%20Peltz's%20Trian%20Fund%20Management%20and%20Blackwells%20Capital%20have%20proposed%20board%20candidates%2C%20who%20Disney%20has%20countered%20with%20its%20own%20proposed%20slate%2C%20supported%20by%20influential%20shareholder%20ValueAct%20Capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20entered%20a%20new%20era%2C%26quot%3B%20Iger%20said%20as%20he%20kicked%20off%20his%20earnings%20call%2C%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20news%20that%20Swift's%20%26quot%3BEras%20Tour%26quot%3B%20film%20will%20be%20exclusively%20available%20on%20Disney%2B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20seemed%20to%20agree%2C%20with%20Disney%20shares%20jumping%20about%207%25%20in%20after-hours%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20are%20on%20Iger's%20side.%20Disney's%20fiscal%20first-quarter%20earnings%20per%20share%20beat%20expectations%20and%20it%20said%20its%20full-year%20EPS%20will%20rise%20at%20least%2020%25%20from%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20narrowed%20its%20streaming%20losses%20to%20%24216%20million%20from%20%241.05%20billion%20in%20the%20prior%20quarter%20and%20expects%20the%20unit%20to%20be%20profitable%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDisney's%20third%20strong%20quarter%20in%20a%20row%20will%20bolster%20Iger%20as%20he%20continues%20to%20grapple%20with%20getting%20the%20streaming%20business%20to%20profitability%2C%20and%20shrinking%20the%20streaming%20losses%20was%20a%20big%20step%20in%20that%20direction%20that%20should%20help%20pull%20the%20stock%20out%20of%20its%20slump%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%20Verna%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Insider%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20still%20big%20battles%20ahead%20for%20Disney%20this%20year%20and%20beyond%2C%20but%20today's%20results%20will%20no%20doubt%20bring%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief%20to%20the%20company's%20leaders%20and%20shareholders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDisney%20to%20invest%20in%20%26quot%3BFortnite%26quot%3B%20maker%2C%20announces%20ESPN%20strategy%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBoosting%20the%20results%20were%20a%20slew%20of%20announcements%20reminiscent%20of%20Ig