ramming%20with%20Fox%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery's.%20Iger%20described%20the%20joint%20venture%20as%20a%20multi-channel%20play%20to%20attract%20new%20customers%20who%20may%20think%20the%20classic%20pay-TV%20bundle%20is%20too%20expensive.%20The%20companies%20haven't%20yet%20announced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-questions-espn-fox-and-wbd-new-sports-streamer-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eprice%20for%20their%20streamer%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Wall%20Street%20is%20curious%20how%20quickly%20these%20new%20efforts%20could%20cannibalize%20and%20replace%20Disney's%20existing%20linear%20TV%20business%20that%20relies%20on%20the%20cable%20bundle%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20Disney%20will%20balance%20investment%20and%20priorities%20between%20the%20two%20sports%20streamers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20there's%20consumer%20demand%2C%20the%20JV%20faces%20several%20hurdles%2C%20from%20challenges%20brought%20by%20existing%20distributors%20to%20antitrust%20opposition%2C%20LightShed%20Partners%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20published%20ahead%20of%20Disney's%20earnings%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Iger%20had%20been%20under%20pressure%20from%20investors%20to%20better%20monetize%20and%20define%20the%20future%20of%20its%20sports%20network%2C%20which%20has%20been%20hit%20by%20cord-cutting%20and%20rising%20sports-rights%20costs.%20Some%20had%20even%20called%20for%20Disney%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fmedia-telecom%2Fdisney-ceo-chapek-rejects-activist-loebs-call-espn-spin-off-ft-2022-09-11%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Espin%20off%20the%20ESPN%20brand%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Challenges%20aside%2C%20the%20new%20sports%20streaming%20strategy%20is%20a%20big%20step%20forward%20for%20Iger%20and%20Disney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BMoana%26quot%3B%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%20may%20be%20Disney's%202024%20MVPs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3