3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Epoison%20gas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20Egypt%20still%20couldn't%20suppress%20the%20rebellion.%20The%20insurgents%20lacked%20arms%2C%20but%20had%20no%20shortage%20of%20desolate%20mountains%20as%20sanctuaries.%20Airpower%20became%20Egypt's%20favored%20weapon%2C%20but%20as%20Russia%20and%20America%20discovered%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20aerial%20bombardment%20could%20not%20compel%20tough%20tribesmen%20to%20lay%20down%20their%20arms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20very%20warlike%2C%20independent%20tribes%20that%20are%20very%20resistant%20to%20foreign%20intervention%20and%20to%20centralized%20rule%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ferris.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Thousands%20of%20Houthi%20supporters%20demonstrate%20to%20show%20solidarity%20for%20Palestine%20against%20the%20ongoing%20Israeli%20attacks%20on%20Gaza%20and%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20airstrikes%20on%20Yemen%20on%20February%207.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3fba07a3d27148878d9e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221366%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThousands%20of%20Houthi%20supporters%20demonstrate%20to%20show%20solidarity%20for%20Palestine%20against%20the%20ongoing%20Israeli%20attacks%20on%20Gaza%20and%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20airstrikes%20on%20Yemen%20on%20February%207.%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Hamoud%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20political%20alignments%20between%201963%20and%202023%20are%20like%20a%20world%20turned%20upside%20down.%20To%20derail%20Nasser's%20secular%20Pan-Arabism%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20fundamentalist%20monarchy%20supported%20the%20Houthi-dominated%20Royalists%2C%20as%20did%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.declassifieduk.org%2Fbritains-covert-war-in-yemen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EBritain%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20who%20feared%20for%20its%20waning%20empire.%20Fast%20forward%20to%202015%20and%20after%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20Houthis%20who%20are%20rebelling%20against%20the%20Yemeni%20government%2C%20while%20being%20bombed%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2015%2Fmar%2F26%2Fsaudi-arabia-begins-airstrikes-against-houthi-in-yemen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3ESaudi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20British%20aircraft.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20biggest%20irony%20of%20all%3F%20Today's%20Houthis%20are%20attacking%20ships%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20%E2%80%93%20and%20hurling%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fisraels-arrow-knocks-down-apparent-houthi-ballistic-missile-headed-for-eilat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Eballistic%20missiles%20at%20Israel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20ostensibly%20in%20response%20to%20Israel's%20military%20operations%20in%20Gaza.%20Yet%20Israel%20supported%20the%20Houthi-dominated%20rebels%20in%20the%201960s.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20incredible%20things%20I%20discovered%20is%20that%20at%20one%20point%2C%20the%20Israelis%20were%20parachuting%20supplies%20to%20the%20Royalists%20in%20Yemen%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ferris.%20%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20was%2C%20pin%20down%20Nasser's%20forces%20in%20Yemen.%26quot%3B%20Indeed%20the%20rebellion%20eased%20Israel's%20lightning%20victory%20in%20the%201967%20Six-Day%20War%2C%20a%20fact%20that%20the%20Houthis%20have%20chosen%20not%20to%20publicize.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYemen's%20history%20is%20a%20kaleidoscope%2C%20but%20it%20still%20provides%20clues%20to%20solving%20today's%20crisis.%20In%20the%2019th%20Century%2C%20the%20Turks%20were%20frustrated%20that%20committing%20several%20divisions%20couldn't%20pacify%20the%20tribes.%20So%20they%20switched%20to%20a%20more%20fruitful%20strategy%20of%20buying%20off%20tribal%20leaders%20with%20money%20and%20government%20jobs.%20Later%2C%20in%20the%2020th%20Century%2C%20desperate%20Egyptian%20officers%20even%20turned%20to%20%26quot%3Breading%20about%20Lawrence%20of%20Arabia's%20techniques%20%5Bfrom%20the%20First%20World%20War%5D%20for%20pacifying%20and%20mobilizing%20the%20tribes%2C%26quot%3B%20Ferris%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20now%2C%20Western%20bombardment%20won't%20coerce%20the%20Houthis%2C%20while%20Western%20boots%20on%20the%20ground%20would%20mean%20an%20endless%20and%20fruitless%20war%20in%20the%20mountains.%20Nor%20does%20the%20fact%20that%20much%20of%20the%20Yemeni%20population%20is%20starving%20and%20dependent%20on%20international%20food%20aid%20seem%20likely%20to%20sway%20the%20Houthi%20leadership%20and%20their%20Iranian%20sponsors.%20Yet%20even%20Iran%20doesn't%20have%20total%20control%20over%20its%20stubborn%20ally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20West's%20best%20strategy%20may%20be%20to%20deal%20with%20Yemeni%20tribal%20leaders%2C%20Ferris%20said.%20And%2C%20to%20let%20nature%20take%20its%20course%20in%20a%20naturally%20fractious%20nation%20where%20even%20the%20Zaydi%20community%20is%20split%20over%20supporting%20the%20current%20Houthi%20leadership%2C%20with%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wilsoncenter.org%2Farticle%2Fwho-are-yemens-houthis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Eincoherent%20ideology%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20chants%20of%20%26quot%3BDeath%20to%20America!%20Death%20to%20Israel!%26quot%3B%20The%20Houthis%20will%20likely%20discover%20that%20it's%20easier%20to%20fight%20against%20a%20government%20than%20become%20one.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BSooner%20or%20later%2C%20the%20Houthis%20will%20probably%20face%20their%20own%20internal%20rebellion%2C%26quot%3B%20Ferris%20said.%3C%2