ads%2F2020%2F03%2F27130749%2F2020_3img21_Mar_2020_PTI21-03-2020_000204B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20judge%20of%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20Courts%20summoned%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20national%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%207).%20It%20issued%20the%20summons%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%2C%20a%20financial%20crimes%20agency%20of%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20filed%20the%20plea%20in%20response%20to%20Kejriwal%20not%20appearing%20for%20questioning%20despite%20it%20having%20issued%20him%20multiple%20summons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20accused%20Kejriwal%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fdelhi-excise-case-court-summons-arvind-kejriwal-on-feb-17-on-eds-plea-regarding-evading-summons%2F1958044%2F%5C%22%3Egiving%20%E2%80%9Clame%20excuses%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20%E2%80%9C%5Bmaking%5D%20out%20a%20false%20defence%E2%80%9D%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20his%20role%20in%20an%20alleged%20excise%20policy%20scam%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FDelhi%2Fkejriwal-issued-ed-summons-for-fifth-time-in-delhi-excise-policy-case%2Farticle67798120.ece%5C%22%3Efor%20the%20fifth%20time%20on%20January%2031%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20skipped%20this%20summons%20as%20he%20did%20the%20previous%20four%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20claimed%20that%20Kejriwal%20%E2%80%9Cintentionally%20disobeyed%E2%80%9D%20every%20summons%20it%20had%20issued%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmaking%20each%20of%20such%20omission%20or%20disobedience%20a%20separate%20offence%E2%80%9D%2C%20PTI%20quoted%20its%20complaint%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20chief%20metropolitan%20magistrate%20Divya%20Malhotra%20said%20that%20Kejriwal%20was%20%E2%80%9Clegally%20bound%E2%80%9D%20to%20attend%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20summons%20in%20person%20and%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Cpurportedly%20failed%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20complaint%20and%20the%20material%20placed%20on%20record%2C%20%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%3C%2Fem%3E%20offence%20under%20Section%20174%20of%20the%20IPC%20is%20made%20out%E2%80%9D%20against%20Kejriwal%2C%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20law%20dealing%20with%20the%20disobedience%20of%20an%20order%20given%20by%20a%20public%20servant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20asked%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20court%20on%20February%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20complaint%2C%20the%20ED%20added%20that%20Kejriwal%20%E2%80%9Cis%20a%20high-ranking%20public%20functionary%20who%20is%20expected%20to%20obey%20the%20law.%20If%20such%20persons%20holding%20such%20high%20officers%20disobey%20the%20law%2C%20then%20it%20will%20set%20a%20wrong%20example%20for%20the%20common%20man%20i.e.%20the%20%3Cem%3Eaam%20aadmi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20also%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20leader%20and%20MLA%20in%20the%20Delhi%20assembly%20Atishi%20said%20the%20party%20would%20explain%20to%20the%20court%20why%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20summons%20against%20Kejriwal%20were%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20respect%20the%20court%20order.%20We%20will%20keep%20our%20side%20before%20the%20court%20on%20why%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20did%20not%20appear%20before%20the%20ED%20on%20the%20five%20summons.%20We%20will%20tell%20the%20court%20how%20the%20five%20summons%20were%20illegal%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FDelhi%2Fexcise-policy-case-court-asks-kejriwal-to-appear-on-february-17-on-eds-plea%2Farticle67821304.ece%5C%22%3Eshe%20said%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20did%20not%20say%20whether%20Kejriwal%20would%20obey%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20summons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20AAP%20leader%20Satyendar%20Jain%20have%20already%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%20Jain%20has%20been%20in%20prison%20for%20around%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707331130000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F27130749%2F2020_3img21_Mar_2020_PTI21-03-2020_000204B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdelhi-court-summons-arvind-kejriwal-february-17%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20local%20judge%20said%20that%20Kejriwal%20was%20%E2%80%9Clegally%20bound%E2%80%9D%20to%20attend%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20summons%20to%20him%20and%20that%20a%20prima%20facie%20offence%20under%20IPC%20Section%20174%2C%20which%20deals%20with%20disobeying%20a%20public%20servant's%20orders%2C%20was%20made%20out%20against%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdelhi-court-summons-arvind-kejriwal-february-17%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uber%20bookings%20beat%20on%20robust%20demand%20for%20rides%2C%20delivery%20during%20holidays%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707329574000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-10%2F06%2Ffull%2F1665020338-3684.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuber-bookings-beat-on-robust-demand-for-rides-delivery-during-holidays-124020701713_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Revenue%20increased%2015%25%20to%20%249.94%20billion%2C%20ahead%20of%20estimates%20for%20%249.78%20billion%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuber-bookings-beat-on-robust-demand-for-rides-delivery-during-holidays-124020701713_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bus