imes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsoren-illegally-acquired-12-land-parcels-in-ranchi-ed-tells-court-101706815419642.html%5C%22%3Eillegally%20acquiring%208.5%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Ranchi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20it%20was%20obtained%20by%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20large%E2%80%9D%20land-grabbing%20%E2%80%9Csyndicate%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20ED%20said%20in%20a%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20court%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20it%20found%20%E2%80%9Cincriminating%20information%E2%80%9D%20in%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20WhatsApp%20conversations%20with%20a%20close%20aide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20WhatsApp%20chat%20not%20only%20includes%20exchange%20of%20confidential%20information%20regarding%20several%20properties%20but%20other%20incriminating%20information%20relating%20to%20transfer%20posting%2C%20sharing%20of%20government%20records%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20out%20of%20which%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20money%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20generated%20and%20transacted%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fhemant-soren-jharkhand-whatsapp-money-transfer-postings-ed-9149182%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20ED%E2%80%99s%20remand%20note%20said%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20sought%20to%20keep%20Soren%20in%20custody%20for%20seven%20more%20days%2C%20saying%20it%20needed%20to%20confront%20him%20with%20certain%20witnesses%20and%20accused%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20special%20court%20judge%20Dinesh%20Rai%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fpmla-court-extends-ed-remand-of-former-jharkhand-cm-hemant-soren-by-five-days%2Farticle67821086.ece%5C%22%3Egave%20the%20ED%20only%20five%20days%E2%80%99%20custody%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20gene