on.%20It%20looks%20like%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20hide%20something%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20full%20majority%20to%20pass%20the%20Bill%2C%20but%20it%20would%20have%20been%20better%20to%20give%20the%20Opposition%20some%20time%20to%20prepare%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20government%20formed%20the%20Justice%20Ranjana%20Prakash%20Desai%20Committee%20to%20develop%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code.%20However%2C%20despite%20submitting%20its%20report%20within%2013%20months%2C%20the%20committee%20did%20not%20publicly%20disclose%20its%20blueprint%20or%20engage%20with%20social%20groups%20or%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20this%20lack%20of%20transparency%20prevented%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20from%20providing%20inputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20party%20wrote%20letters%20to%20the%20committee%20twice%2C%20asking%20for%20the%20draft%2C%20but%20the%20committee%20did%20not%20give%20any%20reply.%20In%20a%20country%20where%20many%20laws%2C%20including%20criminal%20laws%2C%20are%20still%20not%20uniform%2C%20how%20can%20anyone%20give%20their%20views%20on%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20imagination%20only%3F%20If%20the%20committee%20had%20given%20a%20blueprint%2C%20many%20practical%20and%20valuable%20ideas%20would%20have%20come%20to%20the%20fore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20on%20X%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20come%20to%20light%20through%20the%20press%20that%20your%20law%20is%20a%20Bill%20brought%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20providing%20gender%20equality%20to%20women.%20If%20so%2C%20then%20why%20are%20you%20keeping%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20women%20of%20Uttarakhand%20away%20from%20this%20equality%20right%3F%20Were%20the%20women%20belonging%20to%204%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s