nd%20usages%20of%20the%20parties%20permit%20otherwise.%20The%20question%20that%20begs%20for%20an%20answer%20is%2C%20where%20is%20the%20uniformity%20then%3F%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpokesperson%20S.Q.R.%20Ilyas%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20also%20important%20to%20clarify%20that%20last%20July%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20minorities%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%2C%20held%20a%20joint%20press%20conference%20and%20rejected%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20by%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20given%20by%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20against%20fundamental%20rights%20and%20against%20religious%20and%20cultural%20diversity.%20The%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20have%20been%20exempted%20from%20the%20proposed%20Act%2C%20then%20how%20can%20it%20be%20declared%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20when%20the%20state%20has%20a%20significant%20population%20of%20tribals%20and%20many%20exemptions%20have%20been%20given%20to%20the%20majority%20section%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20a%20candidate.%20It%20happens%20that%20the%20real%20target%20of%20the%20law%20is%20only%20Muslims.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamiat%20Ulema-e-Hind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-hindus-kept-out-asaduddin-owaisi-slams-uniform-civil-code-101707291925902.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Muslims%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20compromise%20on%20Shariah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20accept%20any%20law%20that%20is%20against%20Shariah%20because%20a%20Muslim%20can%20compromise%20with%20everything%2C%20but%20he%20or%20she%20can%20never%20compromise%20on%20Shariah%20and%20religion%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Saket%20Gokhale%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtarakhand-tables-ucc-jail-time-for-unregistered-live-in-relationship-exemption-for-tribals%5C%22%3Ecriticised%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20rules%20for%20couples%20in%20a%20live-in%20relationship%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CBJP%20has%20now%20stepped%20into%20people%E2%80%99s%20bedrooms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20TMC%20leader%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20shocking%20provision%20also%20means%20that%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20merely%20living%20together%20will%20have%20to%20prove%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20in%20a%20live-in%20relationship%20in%20case%20some%20vigilante%20or%20lunatic%20files%20a%20complaint.%20The%20BJP%20has%20now%20stepped%20into%20your%20bedrooms%20and%20can%20investigate%20you%20whenever%20it%20feels%20like.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20shocking%20provision%20also%20means%20that%20a%20man%20%26amp%3B%20a%20woman%20merely%20living%20together%20will%20have%20to%20prove%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20NOT%20in%20a%20live-in%20relationship%20in%20case%20some%20vigilante%20or%20lunatic%20files%20a%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20has%20now%20stepped%20into%20your%20bedrooms%20%26amp%3B%20can%20investigate%20you%20whenever%20it%20feels%20like.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOvN0kgVQRV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOvN0kgVQRV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Saket%20Gokhale%20(%40SaketGokhale)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSaketGokhale%2Fstatus%2F1754797437330293081%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Shama%20Mohamed%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Bill%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cshameful%20attempt%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20to%20barge%20into%20the%20personal%20life%20of%20consenting%20adults%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand%20women%E2%80%99s%20groups%20have%20released%20a%20statement%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20seemingly%20being%20uniform%20across%20religions%2C%20the%20Bill%20is%20actually%20criminalising%20and%20regulating%20constitutionally%20acceptable%20behaviours%2C%20like%20adult%20consenting%20cohabitation%2C%20called%20%E2%80%9Clive%20in%E2%80%99%2C%20reducing%20autonomy%20and%20choice%2C%20which%20the%20women%20in%20this%20country%20have%20attained%20through%20concerted%20%2C%20inside%20the%20homes%20and%20on%20public%20platforms.%20Moral%20policing%20measures%20have%20been%20introduced%20in%20this%20regard.%20What%20is%20shocking%20is%20that%20this%20law%20is%20applicable%20even%20to%20those%20living%20outside%20Uttarakhand%2C%20apart%20from%20being%20applicable%20on%20all%20residents%20of%20the%20state%20including%20those%20who%20do%20not%20have%20a%20domicile.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInterestingly%2C%20there%20is%20a%20glaring%20silence%20about%20the%20rights%20of%20queer%20and%20transgender%20persons%20within%20a%20family%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20transgender%20and%20same%20sex%20persons%20to%20marry%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMajorly%2C%20it%20seeks%20to%20introduce%20changes%20in%20the%20provisions%20that%20are%20perceived%20as%20defective%20in%20the%20Muslim%20law%2C%20such%20as%20unequal%20inheritance%2C%20polygamy%20and%20the%20practice%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehalala%3C%2Fem%3E%20(by%20which%20a%20person%20can%20only%20remarry%20his%20divorced%20spouse%20after%20she%20has%20married%20someone%20else%2C%20consummated%20the%20marriage%20and%20thereafter%20obtained%20a%20divorce).%20In%20one%20sense%2C%20the%20Bill%20has%20terminated%20the%20application%20of%20Muslim%20family%20law%20and%20has%20further%20criminalised%20the%20Muslim%20man%20and%20woman%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rules%20under%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20has%20fixed%20the%20minimum%20age%20for%20marriage%20in%20all%20communities%20%E2%80%93%2018%20for%20women%2C%2021%20for%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20mandates%20compulsory%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20and%20punishment%20of%20three%20to%20six%20months%20in%20jail%20for%20failing%20to%20do%20so.%20Adults%20will%20be%20required%20to%20obtain%20consent%20from%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20born%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20will%20be%20considered%20legitimate%20and%20deserted%20women%20will%20be%20entitled%20to%20maintenance%20from%20their%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20also%20imposes%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20child%20marriage%20and%20introduces%20a%20uniform%20process%20for%20divorce.%20The%20Code%20provides%20equal%20rights%20to%20women%20of%20all%20religions%20in%20their%20ancestral%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20registration%20of%20marriage%20is%20mandatory%20for%20all%20religions.%20Unions%20without%20registration%20will%20be%20deemed%20to%20be%20invalid.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707315412000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F04165732%2FUntitled-design-2021-08-04T165720.758.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fopposition-women-muslim-groups-criticise-uttarakhands-passing-of-uniform-civil-code%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'In%20one%20sense%2C%20the%20Bill%20has%20terminated%20the%20application%20of%20Muslim%20family%20law%20and%20has%20further%20criminalised%20the%20Muslim%20man%20and%20woman%2C'%20read%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20Uttarakhand%20women%E2%80%99s%20groups.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fopposition-women-muslim-groups-criticise-uttarakhands-passing-of-uniform-civil-code%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Macron%20leads%20ceremony%20for%20French%20victims%20of%20Hamas%20attacks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707314455000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F17635%2Fproduction%2F_132579759_cd9d63a32c18b6c0b99cf09c1cc63cc03d2a1f0f0_362_4198_23624198x2362.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68226506%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20French%20president%20said%20the%20events%20of%207%20October%20were%20the%20%26quot%3Blargest%20antisemitic%20attack%26quot%3B%20of%20the%2021st%20Century.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68226506%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68226506.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68226506.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Muslims%20Targeted%20in%20128%20Demolitions%2C%20617%20People%20Affected'%3A%20Amnesty%20Reports%20on%20Bulldozer%20Action%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F16172609%2FUntitled-design-2021-07-16T172559.085.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20International%20human%20rights%20organisation%20Amnesty%20International%20has%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20cessation%20of%20the%20widespread%20and%20unlawful%20demolitions%20of%20Muslims%E2%80%99%20homes%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20places%20of%20worship%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20released%20two%20reports%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%207)%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20speak%20up%2C%20your%20house%20will%20be%20demolished%E2%80%99%3A%20Bulldozer%20Injustice%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Unearthing%20Accountability%3A%20JCB%E2%80%99s%20Role%20and%20Responsibility%20in%20Bulldozer%20Injustice%20in%20India%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20document%20the%20punitive%20demolition%20of%20Muslim%20properties%20in%20at%20least%20five%20states%20using%20JCB-branded%20bulldozers%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20hate%20campaign%20against%20the%20minority%20community%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgn%C3%A8s%20Callamard%2C%20Amnesty%20International%E2%80%99s%20Secretary%20General%20expressed%20deep%20concern%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20unlawful%20demolition%20of%20Muslim%20properties%20by%20the%20Indian%20authorities%2C%20peddled%20as%20%E2%80%98bulldozer%20justice%2C%E2%80%99%20is%20cruel%20and%20appalling.%20Such%20displacement%20and%20dispossession%20are%20deeply%20unjust%2C%20unlawful%2C%20and%20discriminatory.%20They%20are%20destroying%20families%20and%20must%20stop%20immediately.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cimmediately%20halt%20the%20de%20facto%20policy%20of%20demolishing%20people%E2%80%99s%20homes%20as%20a%20form%20of%20extra-judicial%20punishment%20and%20ensure%20nobody%20is%20made%20homeless%20as%20a%20result%20of%20forced%20evictions%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20press%20note%2C%20adding%20that%20adequate%20compensation%20is%20given%20to%20all%20those%20affected%20by%20the%20demolitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-unconstitutionality-of-bulldozer-justice%5C%22%3EThe%20Unconstitutionality%20of%20%E2%80%98Bulldozer%20Justice%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20investigations%2C%20between%20April%20and%20June%202022%2C%20authorities%20in%20five%20states%20carried%20out%20demolitions%20as%20a%20form%20of%20%E2%80%98punishment%E2%80%99%20following%20communal%20violence%20or%20protests%20against%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20detail%20128%20documented%20demolitions%2C%20with%20at%20least%2033%20instances%20of%20JCB%E2%80%99s%20equipment%20being%20repeatedly%20used%2C%20affecting%20617%20individuals%20who%20were%20rendered%20homeless%20or%20deprived%20of%20their%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP-ruled%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20reported%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpunitive%20demolitions%E2%80%9D%20at%2056%2C%20the%20reports%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20demolitions%2C%20often%20enacted%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20removing%20illegal%20construction%2C%20violated%20due%20process%20outlined%20in%20domestic%20and%20international%20human%20rights%20law.%20They%20also%20highlighted%20that%20Muslim-concentrated%20localities%20were%20targeted%2C%20while%20Muslim-owned%20properties%20were%20selectively%20demolished%2C%20leaving%20nearby%20Hindu-owned%20properties%20untouched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20not%20the%20only%20vehicles%20used%2C%20JCB%20bulldozers%20have%20become%20the%20brand%20of%20choice%2C%20with%20the%20company%20earning%20nicknames%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98Jihadi%20Control%20Board%E2%80%99%20from%20right-wing%20media%20and%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmnesty%20International%20had%20earlier%20written%20to%20JCB%20regarding%20the%20matter.%20In%20response%2C%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20they%20had%20no%20control%20or%20responsibility%20over%20how%20its%20products%20are%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN%20Guiding%20Principles%20on%20Business%20and%20Human%20Rights%2C%20JCB%20has%20a%20responsibility%20to%20respect%20human%20rights%20and%20conduct%20due%20diligence%20to%20identify%2C%20prevent%2C%20and%20mitigate%20adverse%20human%20rights%20impacts%20linked%20to%20its%20operations%2C%20the%20human%20rights%20group%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20international%20standards%2C%20JCB%20is%20responsible%20for%20addressing%20what%20third-party%20buyers%20do%20with%20its%20equipment.%20The%20company%20must%20stop%20looking%20away%20as%20JCB%20machines%20are%20used%20to%20target%20and%20punish%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20while%20people%20sloganeer%20anti-Muslim%20vitriol%20mounted%20from%20atop%20these%20bulldozers.%20JCB%20cannot%20continue%20to%20evade%20responsibility%20while%20its%20machines%20are%20repeatedly%20used%20to%20inflict%20human%20rights%20abuses%2C%E2%80%9D%20Callamard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publi