y%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20his%20conspicuous%20absence%20from%20the%20ongoing%20protest%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20against%20the%20denial%20of%20funds%20to%20the%20state%20has%20further%20fuelled%20rumours%20of%20a%20rift%20within%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20absence%20is%20particularly%20striking%20given%20Mamata%E2%80%99s%20personal%20commitment%20to%20the%20dharna%20in%20Kolkata.%20Despite%20instructions%20for%20all%20party%20MPs%20to%20participate%2C%20Abhishek%20remained%20in%20Delhi%20for%20parliamentary%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20serving%20his%20constituency%20actively%2C%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fmptrack%2F17-lok-sabha%2Fabhishek-banerjee%5C%22%3Eparliamentary%20engagement%20remains%20low%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20attendance%20record%20reflects%20this%2C%20standing%20at%2014%25%20compared%20to%20the%20national%20average%20of%2079%25%2C%20and%20participation%20in%20two%20debates%20versus%20the%20national%20average%20of%2045.1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20distance%20from%20the%20dharna%2C%20despite%20senior%20leaders%20joining%20Mamata%20to%20spend%20multiple%20nights%20at%20the%20campsite%2C%20suggests%20a%20power%20struggle%20or%20a%20difference%20in%20strategies%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClash%20with%20the%20old%20guard%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tensions%20initially%20started%20in%202022%2C%20when%20two%20conflicting%20candidate%20lists%20surfaced%20for%20the%20municipal%20polls.%20One%20list%20was%20backed%20by%20party%20veterans%20Partha%20Chatterjee%20and%20Subrata%20Bakshi%2C%20and%20the%20other%20made%20by%20I-PAC%2C%20patronised%20by%20Abhishek.%20Mamata%20initially%20endorsed%20the%20Chatterjee-Bakshi%20list%20but%20faced%20challenges%20from%20Abhishek%2C%20who%20overruled%20her%20in%20several%20municipalities%20and%20favoured%20I-PAC-recommended%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20discord%20led%20to%20discontent%20among%20senior%20leaders%20like%20Chatterjee%20and%20Bakshi%2C%20who%20even%20threatened%20to%20step%20down.%20Caught%20between%20the%20old%20guard%20and%20rising%20aspirations%2C%20Mamata%20dissolved%20key%20party%20committees%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20national%20general%20secretary%20position.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20later%20reinstated%2C%20solidifying%20his%20prominence%20and%20his%20de%20facto%20No.%202%20status%20within%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Abhishek%20has%20been%20advocating%20for%20a%20possible%20retirement%20age%20for%20politicians%2C%20mirroring%20practices%20in%20other%20sectors.%20This%20further%20ruffled%20feathers%20among%20seasoned%20party%20members%2C%20who%20perceiving%20it%20as%20a%20veiled%20message%20targeting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20drew%20closer%2C%20the%20debate%20resurfaced.%20Senior%20leaders%20like%20Subrata%20Bakshi%2C%20Firhad%20Hakim%20and%20Sudip%20Bandopadhyay%20expressed%20differing%20views.%20While%20Bakshi%20openly%20encouraged%20Abhishek%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20Hakim%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20younger%20leaders%20learning%20from%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20history.%20Bandopadhyay%E2%80%99s%20comment%20about%20potential%20chaos%20after%20Mamata%E2%80%99s%20departure%20further%20fuelled%20speculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sparked%20a%20counter-offensive%20from%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20camp%2C%20with%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20advocating%20for%20retiring%20older%20leaders%20and%20promoting%20younger%2C%20tech-savvy%20individuals.%20While%20officially%2C%20Abhishek%20claimed%20to%20be%20an%20%E2%80%9Cobedient%20soldier%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20reiterated%20his%20position%20on%20the%20age%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20there%20is%20a%20certain%20age%20of%20retirement%20for%20every%20sector%2C%20it%20should%20be%20the%20same%20for%20politics%20as%20well.%20Yes%2C%20I%20said%20that%2C%20but%20what%20is%20wrong%20with%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%20declared%20Abhishek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20was%20became%20inadvertently%20swept%20into%20the%20discourse%2C%20as%20there%20were%20questions%20about%20whether%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20indirectly%20targeted%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20public%20rally%2C%20she%20announced%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20believe%20in%20showing%20the%20door%20to%20anyone%20who%20reaches%20the%20age%20of%2060.%E2%80%9D%20This%20statement%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20her%20policy%20of%20utilising%20experienced%20bureaucrats%20beyond%20retirement%2C%20was%20interpreted%20by%20political%20observers%20as%20a%20message%20of%20confidence%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cold%20guard%E2%80%9D%20and%20an%20implicit%20rebuke%20to%20those%20proposing%20an%20age%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20struggle%20or%20strategic%20difference%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20just%20before%20the%20panchayat%20poll%2C%20Abhishek%20undertook%20a%20mass%20outreach%20programme%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Nabo%20Jowar%20Yatra%E2%80%99%2C%20crisscrossing%20the%20state%20for%2051%20days%20with%20road%20shows%20and%20public%20meetings.%20While%20he%20is%20largely%20credited%20with%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20success%20in%20the%20panchayat%20poll%2C%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20party%20remained%20hesitant%20to%20accept%20his%20growing%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETMC%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20the%20panchayat%20election%2C%20securing%2051%25%20of%20votes%20and%20winning%20all%20districts%2C%20was%20not%20without%20controversy.%20There%20was%20widespread%20violence%20resulting%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20over%2050%20lives.%20The%20opposition%20raised%20allegations%20of%20the%20party%20using%20government%20resources%20and%20undue%20influence%20from%20Block%20Development%20Officers%20(BDOs)%20to%20sway%20the%20results.%20Over%20a%20thousand%20legal%20cases%20challenging%20the%20election%E2%80%99s%20legitimacy%20have%20been%20filed%20in%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20within%20the%20party%2C%20accustomed%20to%20Mamata%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20view%20the%20party%20as%20synonymous%20with%20her.%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20selection%20of%20candidates%20based%20on%20vote%20count%2C%20alleged%20ballot%20rigging%20and%20formation%20of%20his%20own%20youth-led%20teams%20during%20the%20panchayat%20elections%20sparked%20criticism%20and%20accusations%20of%20sidelining%20established%20members.%20Abdul%20Karim%20Choudhury%2C%20the%20TMC%20MLA%20of%20Islampur%20in%20North%20Dinajpur%2C%20openly%20rebelled%20and%20fielded%20independent%20candidates%20against%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20official%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20should%20not%20have%20been%20given%20so%20much%20responsibility.%20He%20does%20not%20understand%20anything%20about%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Choudhury%2C%20taking%20a%20potshot%20at%20Abhishek.%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20again%20become%20inactive%20if%20one%20particular%20leader%20tries%20to%20control%20the%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20cousin%20Aditi%20Gayen%20wrote%20a%20cryptic%20social%20media%20post%2C%20hinting%20at%20a%20potential%20difference%20within%20the%20family.%20Gayen%20has%20been%20actively%20sharing%20numerous%20posts%20and%20reposts%20related%20to%20Abhishek%2C%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20noticeable%20absence%20of%20any%20reposts%20featuring%20the%20party%20supremo%20on%20her%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22bn%5C%22%3E%E0%A6%AF%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%97%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%20%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%95%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A4%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BE%20%E0%A6%B8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A5%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%20%E0%A6%AA%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BC%20%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BE%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E0%A6%85%E0%A6%AF%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%97%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%