ft%2C%20Mamata%20would%20have%20taken%20drastic%20actions%2C%20such%20as%20removing%20Abhishek%2C%20and%20would%20not%20remain%20silent%20when%20spokespersons%20like%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20constantly%20attack%20senior%20leaders.%20It%20appears%20that%20Mamata%20is%20aligning%20herself%20with%20the%20veteran%20leaders%2C%20but%20she%20is%20also%20signalling%20that%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20has%20control%20over%20the%20organisation%20by%20not%20taking%20any%20action%20against%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20several%20senior%20leaders%20have%20openly%20pledged%20their%20allegiance%20towards%20Mamata%2C%20indicating%20a%20fissure%20within%20the%20organisation.%20Abhishek%2C%20backed%20by%20I-PAC%2C%20attempted%20to%20revamp%20the%20organisation%20and%20build%20his%20own%20loyal%20base%2C%20but%20his%20efforts%20have%20seemingly%20resulted%20in%20the%20emergence%20of%20two%20distinct%20factions%20across%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbhishek%20is%20still%20overseeing%20the%20organisation%2C%20but%20he%20is%20also%20attempting%20to%20manage%20it%20more%20corporately%20by%20removing%20senior%20leaders%20and%20avoiding%20any%20sympathetic%20sentiments.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20had%20to%20step%20forward%20to%20resolve%20the%20discontent%20between%20the%20senior%20and%20junior%20members%2C%E2%80%9D%20observed%20Pal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20on%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDipak%20Adhikari%2C%20the%20actor-turned-MP%20widely%20known%20as%20Dev%2C%20has%20stepped%20just%20down%20from%20all%20governmental%20roles%20in%20his%20constituency.%20Speculation%20is%20rife%20within%20the%20political%20circles%20of%20Kolkata%20about%20the%20potential%20defection%20of%20another%20veteran%20should%20he%20be%20denied%20tickets%20in%20the%20upcoming%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%202021%20election%20victory%2C%20the%20TMC%20has%20faced%20a%20barrage%20of%20corruption%20allegations%2C%20impacting%20its%20image.%20The%20arrest%20of%20former%20education%20minister%20Partha%20Chatterjee%20and%20seizure%20of%20crores%20in%20cash%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20detention%20of%20party%20heavyweight%20Anubrata%20Mondal%20and%20his%20daughter%20in%20a%20cattle%20scam%2C%20have%20jolted%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20arrest%20of%20state%20minister%20Jyoti%20Priya%20Mallick%20and%20a%20series%20of%20raids%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20have%20further%20rattled%20the%20party.%20Mallick%E2%80%99s%20arrest%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20significant%20blow%20to%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20organisational%20strength%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20due%20to%20his%20influence%20in%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district.%20Adding%20to%20the%20woes%2C%20Abhishek%20himself%20faces%20investigation%20for%20money%20laundering.%20This%20relentless%20onslaught%20of%20corruption%20cases%2C%20coupled%20with%20internal%20strife%20over%20succession%2C%20has%20left%20many%20party%20insiders%20apprehensive%20about%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20preparedness%20for%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20still%20maintain%20that%20there%20is%20no%20coordination%20within%20the%20party%20in%20my%20district.%20Whatever%20you%20call%20it%2C%20young%20or%20old%2C%20there%20is%20no%20coordination%20between%20the%20team.%20You%20know%20how%20many%20times%20I%20have%20said%20this%20upstairs.%20If%20Congress%20and%20CPM%20fight%20together%20in%20Murshidabad%2C%20we%20will%20have%20a%20tough%20battle.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20why%20I-PAC%20isn%E2%80%99t%20working%20in%20full%20swing%20this%20time%20like%20in%20other%20elections%2C%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20doing%20surveys%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20outspoken%20MLA%20Humayun%20Kabir%20from%20Murshidabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20political%20observers%20are%20still%20putting%20the%20TMC%20ahead%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Congress%20and%20the%20Left%20%E2%80%93%20the%20three%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20Biswanath%20Chakraborty%20predicts%20a%20strong%20showing%20for%20the%20TMC%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20between%20their%20tactics%20and%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20success%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Trinamool%20Party%20stands%20on%20a%20few%20pillars%20like%20the%20BJP.%20The%20pillars%20are%20Beneficiary%2C%20Religious%20Vote%2C%20Administration%2C%20Money%20and%20Muscle%20Power.%20Trinamool%20is%20the%20second%20richest%20party%20after%20BJP%20and%20gets%20massive%20electoral%20bonds.%20They%20fight%20elections%20on%20these%20pillars.%20They%20will%20do%20much%20better%20than%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20does%20not%20want%20the%20party%20to%20divide%20along%20these%20lines%20before%20the%20crucial%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Mamata%20knows%2C%20as%20does%20Abhishek%2C%20that%20people%20will%20vote%20for%20her%20regardless%20of%20the%20election.%20She%20is%20the%20sole%20face%20of%20the%20TMC%2C%E2%80%9D%20summed%20up%20Pal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Bengali%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707312633000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07162042%2FTMC-collage.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-abhishek-banerjee-lays-low-rumours-rife-on-aunt-nephew-tension-within-tmc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abhishek's%20distance%20from%20Mamata's%20dharna%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20despite%20senior%20leaders%20joining%20the%20CM%20to%20spend%20multiple%20nights%20at%20the%20campsite%2C%20suggests%20a%20power%20struggle%20or%20a%20difference%20in%20strategies%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-abhishek-banerjee-lays-low-rumours-rife-on-aunt-nephew-tension-within-tmc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Nowadays%20I%20Think%20of%20Nehru%20Quite%20a%20Bit'%3A%20PM%20Modi%20on%20Caste%20Census%20in%201.5-Hour%20RS%20Speech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07183604%2FUntitled-design-3-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Conscious%20that%20the%20Opposition%2C%20particularly%20the%20Congress%20has%20doubled%20down%20on%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20his%20reply%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Motion%20of%20Thanks%20to%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Address%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20defended%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20agree%20to%20conduct%20one%20and%20took%20recourse%20to%20invoking%20correspondence%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20prime%20minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENehru%20was%20born%20in%201889%20and%20died%20in%201964.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20made%20the%20demand%20of%20a%20country-wide%20caste%20census%20central%20to%20its%20pitch%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20accused%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20of%20opposing%20the%20development%20of%20lower%20castes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20speech%20that%20lasted%20about%201%20hour%2030%20minutes%2C%20Modi%20accused%20Nehru%20of%20opposing%20reservations%2C%20and%20alluded%20to%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20recent%20assertions%20in%20which%20he%20has%20claimed%20while%20demanding%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20the%20country%20that%20there%20are%20only%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1704485750102765721%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E3%20members%20of%20the%20OBC%20community%20among%20the%2090%20secretaries%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eworking%20in%20the%20government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNowadays%20I%20think%20of%20Nehru%20quite%20a%20bit%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Modi%20as%20he%20went%20on%20to%20read%20a%20translated%20letter%20written%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20prime%20minister%20to%20chief%20ministers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%99I%20dislike%20any%20kind%20of%20reservation%2C%20particularly%20in%20jobs%20and%20services.%20I%20am%20strongly%20against%20anything%20which%20leads%20to%20inefficiency%20and%20second%20rate%20standards%E2%80%99.%20This%20is%20what%20Nehru%20wrote%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20chief%20ministers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%20I%20say%20that%20they%20are%20against%20reservation%20by%20birth.%20Nehru%20used%20to%20say%20that%20if%20SC%2FST%2FOBC%20get%20reservations%20in%20jobs%20then%20the%20standard%20of%20government%20work%20will%20fall.%20Today%20those%20who%20make%20us%20count%20that%20there%20are%20this%20many%20(SC%2FST%2FOBC)%20here%2C%20this%20is%20the%20root.%20They%20had%20stopped%20recruitment.%20Had%20the%20government%20recruited%20at%20that%20time%20and%20promoted%20them%20then%20today%20they%20would%20have%20been%20here%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20alleged%20that%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20words%20are%20%E2%80%9Cset%20in%20stone%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20one-time%20mentor%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bjp.org%2Fpressreleases%2Fwhy-we-are-opposed-communal-reservations-lk-advani%5C%22%3E%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20had%20in%202004%2C%20quoted%20these%20same%20lines%20by%20Nehru%20with%20another%20interpretation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20pointed%20out%20by%20journalist%20and%20writer%20Nilanjan%20Mukhopadhyay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wish%20to%20make%20it%20categorically%20clear%20that%20I%20have%20not%20cited%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20views%20to%20endorse%20them%20in%20their%20entirety.%20The%20BJP%20believes%20that%20reservations%20are%20indeed%20needed%20to%20help%20SCs%2C%20STs%2C%20and%20OBCs%20to%20overcome%20their%20social%20and%20economic%20backwardness.%20The%20point%20we%20wish%20to%20make%20is%20two-fold%3A%20Nehru%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20limitation%20of%20reservations%20as%20the%20sole%20instrumentality%20for%20the%20socio-economic%20uplift%20of%20those%20who%20are%20socially%20and%20economically%20backward.%20Secondly%2C%20and%20more%20relevant%20to%20our%20present%20context%2C%20he%20was%20totally%20opposed%20to%20reservations%20on%20communal%20considerations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Advani%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Modi%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20opposed%20reservations%20for%20SC%2FST%2FOBCs%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20for%20seven%20decades.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Tuesday%20passed%20two%20bills%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Constitution%20(Scheduled%20Castes)%20Order%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20that%20adds%20Valmiki%20community%20as%20a%20synonym%20of%20Chura%2C%20Balmiki%2C%20Bhangi%2C%20and%20Mehtar%20communities%20in%20the%20list%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3B%20and%20the%20the%20Constitution%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Order%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20add%20four%20communities%20to%20the%20ST%20list%20in%20the%20UT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F696088%2Fjammu-kashmir-tribal-paharis-protest-internet%2F%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%3A%20Protests%20Over%20Tribal%20Status%20for%20Paharis%3B%20Admin%20Locked%20Farooq%20and%20Omar%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20Gates%2C%20Says%20NC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmbedkar%2C%20Bharat%20Ratna%20and%20Droupadi%20Murmu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20also%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20ignoring%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20and%20opposing%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%E2%80%99s%20nomination%20to%20the%20post%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20her%20caste.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCongress%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20never%20given%20rights%20to%20SC%2FST%2FOBC.%20Babasaheb%E2%80%99s%20thoughts%20and%20politics%20were%20discarded%20by%20them.%20They%20did%20not%20want%20to%20give%20him%20Bharat%20Ratna%20either.%20That%20too%20was%20conferred%20on%20him%2C%20by%20a%20BJP-supported%20government.%20Not%20just%20this%2C%20Sitaram%20Kesri%20who%20belonged%20to%20a%20backward%20caste%20and%20was%20the%20Congress%20president%2C%20was%20thrown%20onto%20the%20footpath.%20The%20country%20saw%20what%20the%20Congress%20did%20to%20Sitaram%20Kesri%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Modi%20has%20referred%20to%20the%20former%20Congress%20president%2C%20Kesri.%20During%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20election%20campaign%20in%202018%2C%20he%20had%20referred%20to%20Kesri%20as%20a%20Dalit%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-sitaram-kesri-dalit-congress%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cwho%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20complete%20his%20term.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20also%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20opposing%20an%20%E2%80%9CAdivasi%20%3Cem%3Ebeti%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20daughter%2C%20as%20the%20President%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20oppose%20us%20ideologically%2C%20I%20would%20understand.%20But%20it%20was%20not%20ideological.%20Because%20you%20proposed%20a%20candidate%20who%20had%20left%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20referring%20to%20Yashwant%20Sinha%20who%20was%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2F13-opposition-parties-agree-on-yashwant-sinha-as-presidential-poll-candidate%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20opposition%20candidate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20President%20in%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYour%20opposition%20was%20against%20an%20Adivasi%20beti%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20end%20to%20insulting%20the%20President%20even%20now.%20The%20kind%20of%20statements%20that%20have%20been%20made%20against%20the%20President%20from%20their%20leaders%20we%20have%20seen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20said%20that%20the%20NDA%20government%20has%20always%20put%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20first%20and%20the%20flagship%20schemes%20of%20his%20government%20including%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%2C%20Swacchh%20Bharat%20Abhiyan%20were%20all%20targeted%20to%20the%20poor%20who%20belong%20to%20the%20lower%20castes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20narrative%20has%20been%20placed%20here%20to%20negate%20facts.%20Who%20does%20this%20benefit%3F%20You%20are%20losing%20your%20own%20credibility%20in%20this%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSabka%20Saath%20Sabka%20Vikas%20is%20not%20a%20slogan%2C%20it%20is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKarnataka%E2%80%99s%20protest%20over%20tax%20injustice%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELong%20accused%20by%20non-BJP%20state%20governments%20of%20not%20sharing%20tax%20which%20is%20their%20due%2C%20economists%20having%20pointed%20out%20even%2042%25%20that%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20given%20to%20them%20is%20being%20subverted.%20Economist%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funpaid-work-discouraged-workers-essential-services-as-gifts-jayati-ghosh-on-modi-govts-policies%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJayati%20Ghosh%20had%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20managed%20to%20circumvent%20this%20by%20shifting%20a%20lot%20of%20taxes%20onto%20cesses%20and%20surcharges%E2%80%A6%5Bthis%20has%20meant%5D%E2%80%A6that%20in%202022-23%2C%20it%20was%20only%2031%25%20going%20to%20the%20states%2C%20instead%20of%2042%25%20and%20in%202023-24%2C%20only%2030.4%25.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Reporters%20Collective%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Feconomy%2F2024%2F1%2F18%2Fas-pm-indias-modi-secretly-tried-to-massively-cut-state-funds%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehad%20revealed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20CEO%20of%20Niti%20Aayog%20confessing%20as%20to%20how%20%E2%80%9Cimmediately%20after%20becoming%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%202014%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20held%20backdoor%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Finance%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20significantly%20cut%20funds%20allocated%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20states.%20However%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20commission%2C%20an%20independent%20constitutional%20body%20deciding%20states%E2%80%99%20shares%20from%20central%20taxes%2C%20resisted%2C%20and%20Modi%20had%20to%20back%20off.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20said%20in%20the%20House%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20tax%2C%20our%20money!%20What%20language%20is%20being%20used%3F%20This%20is%20dangerous%20to%20the%20future%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20did%20so%20as%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20Karnataka%20government%20with%20MPs%2C%20MLAs%20and%20MLCs%20protesting%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20citing%20tax%20injustice%20to%20the%20state%20and%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20attempting%20to%20break%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20nation%20is%20not%20just%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20for%20us.%20If%20one%20limb%20of%20the%20body%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20function%2C%20the%20entire%20body%20is%20considered%20disabled.%20If%20any%20part%20of%20the%20country%20is%20in%20pain%2C%20it%20should%20be%20felt%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20Similarly%2C%20if%20one%20corner%20of%20the%20country%20is%20not%20getting%20developed%2C%20the%20country%20cannot%20become%20developed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20language%20that%20is%20being%20spoken%20today%2C%20new%20narratives%20are%20being%20built%20to%20break%20the%20country.%20A%20state%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20hit%20the%20streets%20in%20protest.%20What%20can%20be%20a%20bigger%20misfortune%20for%20the%20country%3F%20If%20an%20Adivasi%20child%20from%20Jharkhand%20wins%20an%20Olympic%20medal%2C%20will%20we%20see%20them%20as%20a%20child%20from%20Jharkhand%20or%20from%20India%3F%20What%20are%20we%20saying%3F%20What%20language%20being%20used%3F%20Can%20we%20say%20that%20vaccines%20were%20made%20in%20one%20corner%20so%20cannot%20be%20used%20by%20others%20in%20the%20country%3F%20Such%20a%20mindset%20is%20coming%20out%20of%20a%20national%20party.%20It%20is%20unfortunate!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20approximately%2020%20minutes%20of%20his%20speech%2C%20Modi%20listed%20the%20achievements%20of%20his%20government%2C%20as%20he%20had%20done%20in%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpm-modi-sounds-lok-sabha-poll-bugle-says-bjp-to-get-370-seats%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereply%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E(with%20inputs%20from%20Wire%20Staff)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707312249000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07183604%2FUntitled-design-3-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnarendra-modi-caste-nehru-rajya-sabha%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20reply%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Motion%20of%20Thanks%20to%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Addre