ash-chandra-bose-non-cooperation-movement-2492699-2024-01-23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformulations%20on%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%20and%20Gandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20speaking%20out%20of%20turn%20did%20not%20escape%20notice%20of%20the%20Central%20Control%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CCC%20held%20an%20emergency%20meeting%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20January%2030%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20is%20the%20uncorrected%20transcript%20of%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20deliberations%2C%20circulated%20among%20the%20participants%20for%20comments%2C%20if%20any%2C%20and%20necessary%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CCC%20met%20at%207%20pm.%20A%20two-minute%20silence%20in%20memory%20of%20the%20great%20martyr%20Nathuram%20Godse%20was%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENagpur%20Man%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20We%20have%20no%20fundamental%20quarrel%20with%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20governor%E2%80%99s%20observations%20but%20we%20cannot%20countenance%20this%20unauthorised%20outburst.%20A%20former%20bureaucrat%20cannot%20be%20the%20opening%20batsman%20in%20this%20%E2%80%9Cdemolish%20Gandhi%E2%80%9D%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENorth%20Block%20member%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EIn%20politics%20there%20is%20something%20called%20timing.%20It%20was%20absolutely%20the%20wrong%20time%20for%20the%20governor%20to%20blurt%20out%20what%20he%20did.%20We%20are%20bending%20over%20backward%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20Ram%20Mandir%20euphoria%20and%20here%20is%20this%20man%20going%20off%20on%20a%20tangent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20Block%20proxy%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Boss%20has%20repeatedly%20emphasised%20that%20before%20starting%20a%20new%20controversy%20or%20unveiling%20a%C2%A0%20revised%20history%20project%2C%20there%20should%20be%20widespread%20internal%20consultations.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20this%20%E2%80%9CDemolish%20Gandhi%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20project%20for%20the%20third%20term.%20We%20believe%20the%20governor%20must%20be%20properly%20disciplined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%5BThe%20North%20Block%20member%20asked%20to%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20governor%2C%20who%20is%20travelling%20out%20of%20the%20state.%20After%20some%20delay%2C%20the%20governor%20was%20located.%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENorth%20Block%20member%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20We%20are%20all%20here%20in%20the%20Central%20Control%20Committee%20and%20there%20is%20a%20feeling%20that%20you%20should%20not%20have%20started%20this%20Gandhi%2FBose%20hoo-ha.%20Do%20you%20have%20any%20comments%20for%20us%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGovernor%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20good%20time%20to%20test%20the%20waters.%20Just%20as%20when%20some%20time%20ago%2C%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Home%20Minister%20had%20called%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%9Ca%20%3Cem%3Echatur%20bania%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20he%20backed%20off%20when%20there%20was%20an%20adverse%20reaction.%20My%20understanding%20is%20that%20there%20are%20no%20negative%20comments%20on%20my%20observations.%20I%20feel%20I%20have%20reason%20to%20feel%20vindicated%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENagpur%20Man%20(intervening%20angrily)%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20This%20is%20the%20bloody%20problem%20when%20intelligence%20officers%20start%20meddling%20in%20matters%20entirely%20political.%20Is%20it%20not%20enough%20that%20the%20NSA%20has%20been%20allowed%20to%20poke%20his%20nose%20in%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20businesses%3F%20Must%20now%20another%20former%20IB%20chap%20be%20setting%20the%20political%20agenda%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMisinformation%20Cell%20representative%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20Exactly%2C%20Shriman.%20%C2%A0It%20is%20a%20simple%20rule%20in%20the%20war%20of%20misperceptions%20that%20before%20we%20put%20out%20a%20counterfeit%20narrative%2C%20we%20must%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20some%20semblance%20of%20truth%20and%20that%20the%20person%20putting%20out%20the%20counterfeit%20narrative%20enjoys%20some%20credibility.%20Now%20this%20man%20says%20he%20has%20read%20some%20old%20documents%20in%20the%20IB%20archives.%20Suppose%20the%20secular%20camp%20gets%20another%20former%20IB%20or%20RAW%20chief%20(and%20they%20seem%20to%20be%20crawling%20all%20over%20the%20place)%20to%20call%20his%20bluff%3F%20Then%2C%20a%20very%20important%20and%20potent%20point%20in%20favour%20of%20Bose%20and%20against%20Gandhi%20would%20be%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBoudhik%20Kosh%20prathinidhi%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20I%20think%20by%20now%20we%20all%20must%20have%20realised%20how%20difficult%20and%20long-drawn%20a%20task%20it%20is%20to%20create%20a%20false%20fact.%20To%20label%20the%20Gandhi-led%20freedom%20movement%20a%20non-event%20in%20such%20a%20casual%20manner%20is%20sheer%20stupidity.%20As%20has%20already%20been%20observed%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20task%20for%20a%20former%20policeman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20cannot%20be%20denied%20that%20for%2070%20years%20the%20country%20has%20been%20told%2C%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%2C%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20and%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20which%20led%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%20And%2C%20since%20we%20are%20here%20among%20friends%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20the%20Sangh%20had%20made%20only%20a%20very%20limited%20contribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENorth%20Bloc%20representative%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EAll%20these%20years%2C%20that%20is%20before%202014%2C%20our%20friends%20had%20made%20such%20a%20shrill%20case%20for%20unsealing%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9CBose%20Papers%E2%80%9D.%20This%20has%20now%20been%20done%20and%20it%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20case%20of%20a%20mountain%20and%20a%20mole%20hill.%20The%20point%20is%20that%20Bose%20is%20a%20very%20weak%20peg%20to%20hang%20our%20saffron%20shirt%20on.%20Our%20friends%20in%20West%20Bengal%20overstate%20and%20over-sell%20Bose.%20If%20the%20country%20has%20moved%20beyond%20Nehru%2C%20how%20can%20the%20Bengalis%20remain%20stuck%20on%20Bose%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENagpur%20man%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EThere%20is%20something%20to%20this.%20After%20all%2C%20how%20Bose%20was%20different%20from%20Gandhi%20was%20that%20he%20was%20willing%20and%20did%20use%20violence%20and%20force%20in%20support%20of%20his%20ideology.%20This%20does%20not%20particularly%20impress%20the%20Bengalis%20who%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20all%20kinds%20of%20violence%20%E2%80%93%20first%20by%20the%20CPM%20and%20now%20by%20the%20TMC%20%E2%80%93%20in%20pursuit%20of%20ideological%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20Bloc%20proxy%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EWe%20can%20keep%20on%20talking%3B%20but%20let%20us%20stop.%20I%20want%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20we%20do%20not%20need%20Bose.%3Cem%3E%20And%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20we%20do%20not%20need%20to%20demolish%20Gandhi%20either.%20We%20shall%20simply%20keep%20on%20relegating%20him%20to%20the%20background.%20The%20average%20Hindu%20must%20not%20be%20given%20any%20reason%20to%20think%20negatively%20of%20us.%20Let%20Gandhi%20rest%20peacefully%20at%20Rajghat.%20We%20now%20have%20Ram%20and%20%E2%80%93%20with%20great%20humility%20and%20pride%E2%80%94%20I%20say%2C%20we%20have%20our%20own%20Mahatma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAtmanirbhar%20irregularly%20contributes%20a%20column%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fbyline%2Fatmanirbhar%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFrom%20the%20Vishwavguru%20Archives%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20and%20believes%20that%20ridicule%20and%20humour%20are%20central%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707309770000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F05102020%2FGandhi_and_Bose_at_the_Indian_National_Congress_1938.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fwhen-a-governor-was-rebuked%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20the%20Vishwaguru%20Archives%3A%20The%20Central%20Control%20Committee%20had%20an%20emergency%20meeting%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20January%2030%2C%202024%20to%20discuss%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20governor's%20statements%20on%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Netaji%20Bose.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fwhen-a-governor-was-rebuked%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Marathi%20Bhasha%20Bhavan%3A%20Strengthening%20of%20Culture%20Needs%20Intellectual%20Planning%2C%20Not%20Cement%20and%20Concrete%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FMarine-Drive_Mumbai.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fminister-says-rs-260-cr-will-be-spent-to-build-marathi-bhasha-bhavan-in-mumbai%2F1944463%2F%5C%22%3Edecision%20to%20allocate%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rs%20260%20crore%20for%20constructing%20a%20Marathi%20Bhasha%20Bhavan%20at%20Marine%20Drive%20in%20Mumbai%20appears%20commendable%20on%20the%20surface%2C%20but%20it%20is%20fundamentally%20politically%20motivated.%20Strengthening%20the%20Marathi%20culture%20needs%20social%20and%20intellectual%20planning%2C%20not%20cement%20and%20concrete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20regard%2C%20the%20Kerala%20model%20sets%20a%20positive%20example.%20The%20Kerala%20Sastra%20Sahitya%20Parishad%20is%20known%20for%20translating%20some%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20best%20knowledge%20inputs%20into%20Malayalam%20within%20a%20short%20span%20of%2015%20days%20from%20their%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20library%20and%20Mantralaya%20library%20books%20have%20been%20dumped%20into%20godowns%20for%20years.%20Since%20many%20writers%20are%20unaware%20of%20this%2C%20how%20can%20we%20expect%20a%20protest%20against%20such%20neglect%3F%20Instead%20of%20addressing%20the%20core%20issues%2C%20the%20government%20seems%20to%20be%20silencing%20criticism%20by%20organising%20conferences%20and%20award%20ceremonies%20for%20writers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intellectual%20tradition%20of%20Maharashtra%20is%20being%20undermined.%C2%A0Merely%20constructing%20buildings%20does%20not%20address%20the%20underlying%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20last%20month%2C%20the%20Jagatik%20Marathi%20Parishad%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dthe%2BWorld%2BMarathi%2BConference%26client%3Dfirefox-b-d%26sca_esv%3D7ec80514b65b74c1%26source%3Dlnms%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjeibXev5aEAxU52TgGHbs7CAgQ_AUoAHoECAMQAg%26biw%3D1536%26bih%3D703%26dpr%3D1.25%5C%22%3Eheld%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20World%20Marathi%20Conference%20at%20the%20CIDCO%20exhibition%20centre.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20huge%20facility%2C%20which%20is%20now%20mainly%20used%20for%20marriage%20ceremonies%20and%20sari%20exhibitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conferences%20are%20primarily%20organised%20as%20showpieces%2C%20with%20poor%20results.%20Last%20month%E2%80%99s%20attendance%20was%20notably%20low.%20The%20same%20situation%20was%20observed%20at%20the%20conference%20held%20in%20the%20dome%20at%20the%20National%20Sports%20Club%20of%20India%20in%20Worli.%20This%20is%20municipal%20space%20which%20is%20allocated%20to%20a%20private%20club%2C%20depriving%20common%20people%20of%20access%20to%20a%20public%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20politicians%2C%20even%20a%20library%20building%20is%20real%20estate%2C%20a%20source%20of%20profit.%20Therefore%2C%20construction%20of%20the%20Central%20Library%20building%20has%20been%20mired%20for%20years%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-pwd-to-advise-cancellation-of-kalina-central-library-contract-2988025%2F%5C%22%3Ealleged%20financial%20irregularities%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20intelligentsia%20remains%20silent%20on%20this%20issue%2C%20and%20as%20a%20consequence%2C%20people%20are%20being%20denied%20free%20access%20to%20books%20in%20this%20library.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20a%20new%20building%20is%20needed%20to%20maintain%20the%20archives%2C%20which%20are%20kept%20in%20the%2019th-century%20Elphinstone%20college%20building%20in%20Mumbai.%20This%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20more%20urgent%20task%20than%20constructing%20the%20Bhasha%20Bhavan%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20visited%20the%20college%20building%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20the%20archives%20are%20fine%20with%20their%20valuable%20records%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20and%20the%20Shivaji%20era.%20However%2C%20the%20space%20is%20inadequate%2C%20and%20reaching%20there%20is%20messy.%20Old%20chairs%2C%20tables%2C%20and%20other%20furniture%20are%20dumped%20in%20the%20passage%20and%20adjoining%20areas.%20The%20visit%20was%20truly%20depressing!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20finely%20preserved%20archives%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20in%20Bikaner.%20I%20visited%20there%20last%20year%20during%20a%20conference%20on%20archives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bikaner%20archives%20also%20have%20a%20well-designed%20gallery%20with%20a%20special%20emphasis%20on%20Maratha%20history%20and%20Shivaji%E2%80%99s%20escape%20from%20Agra%2C%20with%20assistance%20from%20the%20Rajputs%20during%20Aurangzeb%E2%80%99s%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20has%20been%20earmarked%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20archives%20at%20the%20Bandra%20Kurla%20Complex%2C%20next%20to%20the%20posh%20gymkhana%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Cricket%20Association.%20However%2C%20no%20work%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20planned%20yet.%20The%20plot%20has%20been%20taken%20over%20by%20Mumbai%20metro%20railway.%20Notably%2C%20all%20major%20cities%20have%20new%20or%20improved%20buildings%20dedicated%20for%20preserving%20the%20archives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20government%20was%20serious%20about%20promoting%20Marathi%20culture%2C%20it%20could%20have%20easily%20created%20a%20Bhasha%20Bhavan%20in%20a%20six-storey%20building%20it%20built%20last%20year%20behind%20Ravindra%20Natya%20Mandir%20in%20Prabhadevi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20or%20elsewhere.%20Instead%2C%20most%20of%20the%20space%2C%20barring%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20Board%20for%20Literature%20and%20Culture%2C%20is%20allotted%20for%20commercial%20enterprises%2C%20which%20is%20strange%20by%20any%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20building%20at%20Marine%20Drive%20may%20look%20aesthetically%20fine%2C%20with%20P.K.%20Das%20as%20the%20architect%2C%20but%20language%20promotion%20needs%20inputs%20to%20transform%20it%20into%20a%20hub%20of%20modern%20knowledge%20and%20thought.%20The%20Maharashtra%20government%20seems%20to%20have%20no%20imagination%2C%20no%20blueprint%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20space%20in%20the%20prime%20area.%20It%20may%20be%20used%20as%20a%20good%20place%20to%20relax%20for%20politicians%20and%20bureaucrats%20as%20it%20is%20halfway%20between%20Mantralaya%20and%20Malabar%20Hill%2C%20the%20areas%20of%20political%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20strong%20foundation%20for%20the%20promotion%20of%20Marathi%20culture%20and%20knowledge%20was%20established%20in%20the%20newly%20formed%20Maharashtra%20state%20in%201960%20by%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%20Y.B.%20Chavan.%20He%20had%20been%20deeply%20influenced%20by%20modern%20thought%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Laxmanshastri%20Joshi%2C%20a%20scholar%20who%20followed%20the%20teachings%20of%20M.N.%20Roy%2C%20a%20revolutionary%20and%20philosopher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChavan%20initiated%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Vishwakosh%20multi-volume%20Marathi%20encyclopedia%20and%20the%20Maharashtra%20Board%20for%20Literature%20and%20Culture%2C%20which%20published%20several%20important%20scholarly%20books%20at%20low%20prices.%20Some%20of%20the%20best%20work%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20modest%20premises%20in%20the%20holy%2C%20picturesque%2C%20riverside%20town%20of%20Wai%20in%20Satara%20district.%20So%20one%20does%20not%20need%20posh%20spaces%20for%20such%20endeavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fdate%5C%22%3EVidyadhar%20Date%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20a%20cultural%20critic%20and%20the%20author%20of%20a%20book%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20public%20transport.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707309056000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FMarine-Drive_Mumbai.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fmarathi-bhasha-bhavan-strengthening-of-culture-needs-intellectual-planning-not-cement-and-concrete%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Funds%20are%20being%20directed%20towards%20constructing%20buildings%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Marathi%20Bhasha%20Bhavan%20at%20Marine%20Drive%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20yet%20the%20allocation%20lacks%20substantial%20investment%20in%20social%20initiatives%20crucial%20for%20the%20promotion%20of%20Marathi%20culture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fmarathi-bhasha-bhavan-strengthening-of-culture-needs-intellectual-planning-not-cement-and-concrete%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20has%20former%20Fox%20News%20host%20Tucker%20Carlson%20said%20on%20Putin%2C%20the%20war%20and%20Ukraine%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707307380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-tucker-carlson-fox-news_6446884.jpg%3F20240206221743%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhat-has-former-fox-news-host-tucker-carlson-said-on-putin-the-war-and-ukraine-13066018%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Controversial%20right-wing%20US%20journalist%20Tucker%20Carlson%20will%20shortly%20release%20an%20interview%20he%20conducted%20with%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A259%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhat-has-former-fox-news-host-tucker-carlson-said-on-putin-the-