wishers%20worldwide.%20The%20monarch%20ascended%20to%20the%20British%20throne%20at%20the%20age%20of%2073%20following%20the%20death%20of%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II%20on%20September%208%2C%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrince%20William%2C%2041%2C%20the%20eldest%20son%20of%20the%20King%20and%20heir%20to%20the%20throne%2C%20returned%20to%20his%20royal%20duties%20this%20week%20after%20taking%20time%20off%20following%20his%20wife%20Princess%20Kate's%20abdominal%20surgery.%20Prince%20Harry%2C%20who%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Meghan%20Markle%20abdicated%20their%20royal%20titles%20in%202020%20and%20moved%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20is%20en%20route%20to%20London%2C%20having%20been%20informed%20of%20his%20father's%20condition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20royal%20commentator%20Ian%20Pelham%20Turner%20shared%20exclusive%20insights%20with%20NDTV%20on%20how%20the%20royal%20family%20is%20functioning%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20said%20that%20he%20is%20at%20the%20moment%20able%20to%20continue%20looking%20at%20the%20red%20boxes%2C%20the%20official%20boxes%20that%20government%20departments%20send%20to%20him.%20It%20is%20thought%20that%20he%20is%20hoping%2C%20before%20too%20long%2C%20he%20will%20be%20back%20in%20public%20view%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Turner%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fking-charles-diagnosed-with-cancer-says-buckingham-palace-5001016%5C%22%3EKing%20Charles%20Diagnosed%20With%20Cancer%2C%20Says%20Buckingham%20Palace%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%20at%20the%20moment%20what%20would%20happen%20is%20the%20other%20members%20of%20the%20royal%20family%20like%20Queen%20Camilla%20will%20start%20taking%20in%20some%20of%20the%20events%20scheduled%20for%20the%20King.%20The%20King%20will%20also%20have%20his%20audience%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20which%20he%20has%20every%20Wednesday.%20Queen%20Camilla%20has%20already%20taken%20up%20some%20of%20the%20royal%20duties%20that%20the%20King%20normally%20faces%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20King%20Charles%20garnered%20praise%20for%20his%20candidness%20in%20discussing%20a%20prostate%20condition%2C%20prompting%20an%20increased%20awareness%20among%20the%20public%20about%20similar%20health%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20from%20various%20nations%20expressed%20their%20well-wishes%20for%20a%20swift%20recovery%20for%20the%2075-year-old%20King.%20Prime%20Minister%20Sunak%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20and%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20are%20among%20the%20many%20voices%20sending%20messages%20of%20solidarity%20to%20King%20Charles%20and%20the%20British%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20speculation%20about%20the%20line%20of%20succession%2C%20Mr%20Turner%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20King%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20give%20up%20his%20throne%20in%20way%2C%20shape%20or%20form.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20London%2C%20citizens%20expressed%20shock%20and%20sympathy%20at%20the%20news%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20weight%20of%20a%20cancer%20diagnosis%20for%20anyone%2C%20even%20a%20figure%20as%20prominent%20as%20King%20Charles.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707194280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-10%2F9a6oea9o_prince-charles-william-harry-instagram_625x300_23_October_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-royal-commentator-told-ndtv-after-king-charles-iiis-cancer-diagnosis-5003045%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UK's%20King%20Charles%20III%20is%20undergoing%20treatment%20for%20cancer%2C%20triggering%20an%20outpouring%20of%20support%20from%20well-wishers%20worldwide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-royal-commentator-told-