%3ESocial%20innovation%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Social%20innovation%20offers%20inventive%20technological%20solutions%20to%20societal%20issues%2C%20empowering%20local%20communities%20and%20addressing%20diverse%20needs.%20Prioritising%20sustainability%20and%20scalability%2C%20these%20innovations%20aim%20for%20enduring%20impacts%20adaptable%20to%20various%20situations%2C%20significantly%20contributing%20to%20multiple%20SDGs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollaborative%20partnerships%20among%20private%20entities%2C%20NGOs%2C%20and%20governments%20drive%20equity%20and%20extend%20development%20initiatives%20to%20marginalised%20groups%2C%20providing%20a%20boost%20in%20the%20race%20towards%20SDGs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECollaboration%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Collaborative%20efforts%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20shared%20goal%20of%20leveraging%20technology%20for%20positive%20change%2C%20are%20crucial%20for%20SDG%20achievement.%20Bringing%20together%20expertise%20from%20governments%2C%20businesses%2C%20NGOs%2C%20academia%2C%20and%20communities%20allows%20for%20comprehensive%20problem-solving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20collective%20perspective%20on%20using%20digital%20innovation%2C%20data-driven%20solutions%2C%20and%20connectivity%20tools%20amplifies%20efforts%20to%20advance%20the%20SDGs%2C%20making%20collaboration%20the%20binding%20agent%20for%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20really%20struck%20me%20while%20building%20tech%20startups%20was%20the%20idea%20of%20how%20one%20could%20build%20an%20internet-based%20company%20to%20drive%20large-scale%20social%20change.%20Citizens%20want%20to%20be%20inspired.%20The%20need%20to%20be%20inspired%20is%20a%20universal%20need.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20storytelling.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20how%20you%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282876%2Frobinson-crusoe-island-taught-me-about-sustainability-storytelling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20a%20story%20relatable%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20average%20citizen%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dhimant%20Parekh%2C%20Founder%20and%20CEO%2C%20The%20Better%20India%20%E2%80%94%20one%20among%20the%20over%2080%20notable%20speakers%20and%20delegates%20present%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20message%20from%20the%20conclave%20is%20that%20combining%20technology%20with%20collaborative%20efforts%20can%20speed%20up%20progress%20in%20education%2C%20climate%20action%2C%20poverty%20reduction%2C%20and%20achieving%20at%20least%2070%25%20of%20the%20169%20SDG%20targets%20using%20data%20and%20digital%20technologies.%20This%20needs%20urgent%20action%20and%20a%20united%20effort%20from%20stakeholders%20like%20government%2C%20organisations%2C%20communities%2C%20and%20individuals.%20Effective%20strategies%2C%20policies%2C%20and%20initiatives%20are%20essential%20to%20accelerate%20the%202030%20agenda%20for%20sustainable%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20as%20a%20country%20is%20extremely%20committed%20to%20using%20technology%20and%20leveraging%20DPIs%20to%20fast-track%20the%20SDGs%2C%20and%20also%20to%20share%20our%20experiences%20and%20expertise%20with%20the%20global%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Abhishek%20Singh%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706796173000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDSC_4404-min_11zon-1706795984-scaled.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340504%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TechForGood%20India%20Conclave%202024%2C%20aligned%20with%20UN%E2%80%99s%202030%20SDG%20Agenda%2C%20emphasises%20on%20collaborative%20efforts%20to%20overcome%20challenges%20hindering%20SDG%20progress%20in%20India.%20The%20conclave%2C%20focusing%20on%20sustainability%2C%20digital%20equity%2C%20and%20social%20innovation%2C%20highlighted%20collaborative%20partnerships%20for%20SDG%20success.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Pranita%20Bhat%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340504%2Fnasscom-foundation-techforgood-conclave-new-delhi-achieve-sdg-success-digital-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IAS%20Officer%20Uses%20IoT%20to%20Raise%20Water%20Supply%2C%20Cut%20Power%20Bills%20by%2040%25%20in%2016%20Villages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EErode%20district%2C%20which%20lies%20in%20the%20western%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289205%2Frainwater-harvesting-system-in-tamil-nadu-helps-village-during-cyclone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20region%20characterised%20by%20limited%20rainfall%2C%20dry%20climate%20and%20erratic%20water%20supply.%20For%20the%20approximately%2011%20lakh%20residents%20of%20the%20district%20who%20reside%20in%20its%20rural%20areas%20(as%20per%202011%20Census)%2C%20this%20irregular%20water%20supply%20is%20an%20even%20bigger%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20district%20administration%2C%20while%20the%20rural%20water%20demand%20in%20the%20district%20is%2074%20MLD%20(million%20litres%20a%20day)%2C%20the%20water%20supplied%20is%20approximately%2040%20to%2055%20LPCD%20(litres%20per%20capita%20per%20day).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20water%20is%20supplied%20from%20the%20Kaveri%20and%20Bhavani%20rivers%20through%2020%20Combined%20Water%20Supply%20Schemes%20(i.e.%20water%20from%20rivers)%20apart%20from%20local%20borewell%20sources.%20Currently%2C%20most%20villages%20in%20Erode%20district%20and%20elsewhere%20rely%20on%20overhead%20tanks%20(OHTs)%20for%20their%20water%20supply%2C%20sourced%20either%20from%20borewells%20or%20infiltration%20wells%20in%20nearby%20rivers%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20District%20Collector%20(DC)%20Raja%20Gopal%20Sunkara%2C%20a%202015-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDC%20Sunkara%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%20that%20in%20the%20Erode%20district%2C%20there%20are%20over%204%2C700%20Over%20Head%20Tanks%20(OHTs)%20in%20rural%20areas%20whereas%20the%20number%20of%20tank%20operators%20is%20only%20299.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20reliance%20on%20tank%20operators%2C%20he%20explains%20the%20following%20problems%20were%20being%20faced%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20High%20water%20losses%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CIn%20most%20villages%2C%20we%20see%20overflowing%20OHTs%20since%20the%20motors%20are%20not%20switched%20off%20on%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20DC%20Sunkara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Unreliable%20timings%20of%20water%20supply%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Since%20tank%20operators%20have%20to%20manually%20manage%20OHTs%2C%20water%20supply%20timings%20change%20from%20day%20to%20day%20depending%20on%20their%20availability%20and%20punctuality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20High%20electricity%20bill%20for%20the%20local%20body%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20motors%20are%20not%20switched%20off%20on%20time%2C%20the%20electricity%20bills%20of%20villages%20increase%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Dry%20Run%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Motors%20get%20damaged%20when%20they%20are%20run%20without%20water%20in%20the%20sump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20K%20Renuva%20Devi%2C%20the%20Panchayat%20president%20of%20Kuttapalayam%20village%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20were%20dependent%20on%20the%20tank%20operator%2C%20who%20used%20to%20manually%20operate%20the%20gate%20valves%20and%20motor%20pumps.%20There%20used%20to%20be%20overflow%20from%20the%20tanks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20these%20failings%20of%20the%20OHT%20water%20supply%20system%20in%20Erode%20district%2C%20DC%20Sunkara%20has%20installed%20IoT%20devices%20in%205