%20with%20individual%20courtyards%20in%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20furniture%20arrangement%20was%20also%20crucial%2C%20and%20the%20shape%20and%20size%20of%20the%20classrooms%20evolved%20based%20on%20how%20students%20would%20sit.%20To%20ensure%20equal%20attention%20from%20the%20teacher%2C%20we%20designed%20a%20%E2%80%98C%E2%80%99%20shaped%20seating%20arrangement%20where%20each%20student%20is%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20the%20teacher%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20also%20believed%20that%20the%20children%20should%20also%20get%20the%20chance%20to%20learn%20outdoors%2C%20hence%20he%20included%20the%20courtyards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20recognised%20that%20learning%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20only%20happen%20within%20the%20classroom%20but%20extends%20beyond%20its%20walls.%20Considering%20this%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20courtyards%20became%20crucial.%20In%20addition%20to%20their%20educational%20significance%2C%20there%20were%20practical%20reasons%20for%20incorporating%20courtyards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20area%20experiences%20a%20hot%20and%20dry%20climate%2C%20which%20can%20be%20challenging%20for%20students%20with%20low%20vision%20sensitive%20to%20direct%20light.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20we%20ensured%20that%20the%20courtyard%20provides%20filtered%20light%20to%20the%20classrooms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndirect%20light%20was%20a%20significant%20concern%20as%20the%20architect%20aimed%20to%20provide%20a%20comfortable%20learning%20environment%20for%20low-vision%20students%20with%20minimal%20glare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20protect%20the%20low-vision%20students%20from%20direct%20light%20glare%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318714%2Ftamil-nadu-engineer-turns-artist-paints-with-sunlight-vignesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrin