h%20brands.%20Since%20my%20channel%20skyrocketed%20in%20just%20two%20or%20three%20weeks%2C%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20brand%20promotions%20and%20earned%20much.%20But%20brands%20have%20begun%20approaching%20me%20to%20make%20promotional%20videos.%20Things%20haven%E2%80%99t%20changed%20much%20for%20me%20%5Bmaterially%20speaking%5D%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20this%20is%20going%20to%20change%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20earning%20good%20money%20through%20his%20work%20online%20would%20be%20beneficial%20but%20the%20reason%20Dhiraj%20makes%20these%20reels%20is%20because%20he%20wants%20to%20develop%20his%20communication%20skills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20as%20I%20said%20earlier%2C%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20to%20do%20that%20is%20by%20teaching%20it%20%5Bconversational%20English%5D%20to%20people.%20Through%20this%2C%20you%20are%20not%20only%20helping%20people%20grow%20but%20also%20growing%20yourself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20longer%20videos%20but%20since%20people%20these%20days%20watch%20a%20lot%20of%20shorts%2C%20I%20thought%20making%20these%20reels%20was%20a%20way%20to%20earn%20a%20greater%20following.%20Since%20my%20content%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20people%20have%20been%20asking%20me%20to%20make%20longer%20videos%20on%20how%20to%20speak%20English.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20develop%20a%20course%20for%20people%20which%20will%20probably%20start%20in%20a%20few%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(You%20can%20watch%20more%20of%20Dhiraj%20Takri%E2%80%99s%20content%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdhirajtakri%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Instagram%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Dhiraj%20Ta