%5D.%20He%20was%20driving%20his%20Swift%20at%20speeds%20close%20to%2090%20km%2Fhr%20to%20100km%2Fhr.%20Police%20followed%20him%20on%20four%20bikes%20and%20four%20vans.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20main%20suspect%20dropped%20his%20girlfriend%20at%20her%20residence%2C%20the%20police%20continued%20trailing%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestatesman.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fkidnapper-shot-dead-two-held-5-year-old-rescued-1502580909.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Dr%20Naik%20added%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAround%2012.30%20am%2C%20Nitin%20was%20intercepted%20near%20a%20community%20block%20in%20Seemapuri%20%5Bnear%20the%20Delhi-UP%20border%5D.%20Before%20his%20vehicle%20stopped%2C%20he%20hit%20our%20vehicle%20and%20he%20was%20drunk.%20He%20was%20also%20carrying%20three%20mobile%20phones.%20On%20interrogation%2C%20he%20told%20police%20that%20two%20of%20his%20friends%20had%20kept%20the%20child%20in%20a%20flat%20in%20Shalimar%20City%20in%20Sahibabad.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20the%20main%20suspect%20to%20confess%20where%20they%20were%20keeping%20the%20boy%2C%20there%20were%20discussions%20among%20senior%20officers%20who%20were%20informed%20of%20the%20interception%20that%20they%20should%20wait%20to%20gather%20more%20force%20(personnel).%20Dr%20Naik%20disagreed%20and%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20time%20and%20they%20needed%20to%20move%20fast%20with%20the%20suspect%20in%20their%20custody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20his%20phones%20are%20with%20us%20and%20if%20he%20is%20unreachable%2C%20his%20accomplices%20may%20get%20alerted%2C%20leave%20the%20apartment%2C%20and%20possibly%20harm%20the%20boy%20as%20well.%20Thankfully%2C%20my%20top%20boss%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Crime%20Branch%20trusted%20my%20instincts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Ram-Gopal-Naik-IPS-Officer-Image-5-1706534343.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Serving%20IPS%20officer%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Ram-Gopal-Naik-IPS-Officer-Image-5-1706534343.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Ram-Gopal-Naik-IPS-Officer-Image-5-1706534343-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Ram-Gopal-Naik-IPS-Officer-Image-5-1706534343-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Ram-Gopal-Naik-IPS-Officer-Image-5-1706534343-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Ram-Gopal-Naik-IPS-Officer-Image-5-1706534343-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339981%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDCP%20Dr%20Ram%20Gopal%20Naik%2C%20a%202002-batch%20IPS%20officer%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20barely%201.5%20hours%2C%20Dr%20Naik%E2%80%99s%20team%20reached%20the%20apartment%20complex%2C%20did%20a%20complete%20recce%20of%20it%2C%20covered%20all%20the%20exits%2C%20got%20into%20the%20flat%20amidst%20a%20firefight%2C%20and%20rescued%20the%20boy.%20To%20understand%20the%20layout%20of%20the%20two-bedroom%20apartment%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20and%20two%20other%20officers%20visited%20another%20apartment%20in%20the%20same%20complex%20and%20asked%20the%20family%20residing%20inside%20if%20they%20could%20take%20a%20look.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20understood%20the%20layout%20of%20this%20apartment%2C%20we%20took%20positions%20outside%20the%20fifth-floor%20flat%20where%20the%20child%20was%20being%20kept.%20Meanwhile%2C%20we%20also%20had%20a%20team%20prepared%20below%20with%20blankets%20and%20nets%20ready%20in%20case%20the%20kidnappers%20tried%20to%20throw%20the%20boy%20off%20the%20balcony.%20At%20this%20crucial%20juncture%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20send%20the%20suspect%20to%20ring%20the%20bell%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20suspect%20Nitin%20proceeded%20to%20ring%20the%20bell%2C%20but%20the%20moment%20his%20accomplice%20opened%20the%20door%20he%20sensed%20that%20something%20was%20wrong%20and%20tried%20to%20shut%20it%20immediately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20he%20was%20about%20to%20shut%20the%20door%2C%20I%20told%20one%20of%20my%20officers%20that%20we%20had%20to%20break%20these%20doors%20down.%20Luckily%2C%20there%20was%20a%20little%20gap%20on%20top%20of%20the%20iron%20grill%20door.%20One%20of%20my%20officers%20was%20able%20to%20bend%20the%20iron%20grill%20part%20of%20the%20door%20down%20and%20that%20left%20enough%20space%20for%20me%20to%20enter.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20kidnappers%20inside%20began%20firing%20at%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20As%20per%20news%20reports%2C%20a%20bullet%20hit%20Inspector%20Vinay%20Tyagi%E2%80%99s%20vest%2C%20while%20another%20hit%20commando%20Kuldip%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20this%20chaos%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20climbed%20over%20the%20bent%20iron%20grill%20and%20took%20a%20peek%20at%20the%20gap%20left%20behind%20by%20a%20second%20wooden%20door%20inside%20to%20see%20if%20the%20child%20was%20inside%20the%20main%20hall%20of%20the%20flat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20the%20boy%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20there.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20ordered%20the%20personnel%20behind%20me%20to%20fire%20back.%20There%20was%20an%20exchange%20of%20fire.%20One%20of%20the%20kidnappers%20was%20shot%20down%20on%20the%20ground%20lying%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20blood%20while%20the%20other%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20leg.%20My%20team%20immediately%20followed%20me%20inside%20while%20I%20went%20straight%2